\id ACT - Aruamu trans by Steven, Siria, Obnadum, Francis; exegetical check by John/Marsha Relyea and full Aruamu team; comprehension check by 3 groups; consultant check by Norm Mundhenk. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus.
\h Aposel
\toc3 AP
\toc2 Aposel
\toc1 Aposelbar Ingangariba
\mt1 Aposelbar Ingangariba
\mt2 O
\mt1 Aposel
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, Aposelbar Ingangariba, Lukra an osiri. Luk faragha, ak…®nafarir igharazim osiri, a Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n Aposelbar Ingangariba osiri.
\ip E ak…®nafarir kam…®n garima, God…®n Duam aposelba tuavim men akaz…®, me Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven ko, Judian danganiba bar mogh…®ra ko, Samarian Distrik ko, nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar,‚Äù an gun me m…®gei. (N…® sapta 1:8…®n gan.)
\ip Aposelbar ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Iesus…®n sios Judabar tong…®n d…®kavigha egha g…®n ghua bar ekevegha tintinibar ghua nguazim…®n otevir mabar ghu. Luk uaghan kamagh…®n en akaghasa, Krais…®n ingangarim ko gumazamizir an g…®n zuibar dabirabim, da God fom…®ra Israel…®n gumazamiziba bagha d…®k…®r…®zir akam bar a ko vorogh…®ra ghu.
\ip Ez…® bizir ekiar mam Aposelbar ak…®nafarim a m…®gei, a God…®n Duam…®n ingangarim. Pentikos…®n dughiam…®n God…®n Duam faragha Iesus…®n suren gumazamizibar ize. Egha g…®n God…®n Duam n…®ghn…®ziba me gan…®ga, egha gavgavim me gan…®di.
\ip Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam e uaghan aposelbar akar ruarir av…®ribar gari. Dughiar av…®riba aposelba Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim gumazamizir igharazibav k…®nasa. Ez…® e garima gumazamizir av…®rim Akar Aghuir kam…®n g…®n zui, ez…® sios otogha gavgafi.
\ip Aposelbar ak…®nafarim, an aposel…®n av…®ribar eghaghaniba an iti. Egha akar bar av…®riba, Pita ko Pol amizir bizibav gei. Pita a suren gumazir mam, a uaghan Iesus ko arui. Ez…® Pol faragha Iesus…®n g…®n aruizir puvat…®. A Iesus…®n sios…®n gumazamiziba d…®kab…®nasa pamtem…®n ingari. Ez…® Iesus Pol…®n diaz…®, a Iesus baghav…®ra itir gumazim…®n m…®n otogha guizbang…®ra an ingangarim pamtem a gami.
\ip Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n otevir maba, Luk bizir Pol bativizibagh eghanasa, ghaze, ‚ÄúEia,‚Äù e dagh ami. Fofozir gumazir av…®rim ghaze, Luk uab…® ti Pol ko dughiar mabar arui, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ghaze, ‚ÄúEia.‚Äù
\c 1
\ms1 Aposelba Jerusalem…®n aven Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim akuri
\mr (Sapta 1:1--8:3)
\s1 Iesus akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n ghaze, a God…®n Duam amangam
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Mak 16:19; Luk 1:1-4; 24:49-51\x*Tiofilus, k…® ak…®nafarir kam n…® bagha an osiri. Nan ak…®nafarir faragha zuim…®n, k…® Iesus amizir biziba ko, a gumazamizibar sure gamiziba bar, ada osiri. Dughiar kam…®n Iesus d…®kavigha uan ingangarim gamua mamagh…®ra ikia, ghua a God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabozir dughiam…®n tuzir biziba, k…® da osiri. A t…®ghar God…®n Nguibam…®n mangasa, aposelba m…®sevegha God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n ingangarir akabar me m…®gei.\f + \fr 1:1-2 \ft Luk, a ak…®nafarir kam Aposelbar Ingangariba, an osiri. A faragha zuir ak…®nafarim an osiriz…®, a Luk Osirizir Akar Aghuim.\f*
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Matyu 28:17; Mak 16:12; Luk 24:36-49; Aposel 10:41; 1 Korin 15:5-7\x*A faragha m…®zaziba inigha aremegha ua d…®kafi. Egha a t…®ghar God…®n Nguibam…®n mangasava amua uab…® isa uan aposelbar aka. Egha a bizir av…®ribar men akaz…®, me bar fo, a ua d…®kavigha iti. Ez…® 40plan dughiaba, dughiar kam…®n aven dughiar av…®riba a uab…® men akakaghava God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n gun me m…®gei.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Luk 24:49; Jon 14:16-17; Aposel 2:33\x*Dughiar mam…®n a me ko ikia, apava m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavir kam me gan…®ngi, ‚ÄúIa Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ategh mangan mark…®. Bizir aghuarir nan Afeziam ia dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizim a izam. K…® an gun ia m…®kemez…®, ia a baraki. Ia a bagh ik…®.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Matyu 3:11; Mak 1:8; Luk 3:16; Jon 1:33; Aposel 11:16\x*Jon d…®pam…®n gumazamiziba rue, ez…® gurumra ia God…®n Duam…®n ruegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Aisaia 1:26; Amos 9:11; Matyu 24:3; Luk 24:21\x*Ez…® me uari akuvazir dughiam…®n, me an azara, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® dughiar kam atrivim Israel danight…®ma, a ua Israel…®n nguazim…®n ganam, o?‚Äù\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Fom…®ra Israel…®n gumazir maba uari atrivim…®n ikia uan nguazim…®n gari. Egha Iesus…®n dughiam…®n Israelia Rom…®n apengan iti. Ez…® Iesus dughiar kam…®n otogha aruima, gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a Rom…®n gavman batuegh…®va uab…® Israelian ganam. Eght…® g…®n Israel Kantrin igharaziba dar gan…®va egh dar apengan ikian kogham.\f*
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Matyu 24:36; Mak 13:32; 1 Tesalonika 5:1\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúBiziba otivamin dughiaba, nan afeziam uab…® uan gavgavim…®n da at…®. Ez…® ia tizim bagh dughiar an at…®zir kam g…®foghasa. Kar ian bizim puvat…®.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Matyu 28:19; Mak 16:15; Luk 24:47-48; Jon 15:27; Aposel 2:32; 3:15; 5:32\x*God…®n Duam izighir…® ia giz…®vaght…®, ia an gavgavim iniam. Eght…® bizir ia ganigha foziba, ia Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven ko, Judian danganiba bar mogh…®ra ko, Samarian Distrik ko, nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar, me geghanam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n zui
\r (Mak 16:19-20; Luk 24:50-53)
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Mak 16:19; Luk 24:50-51; Jon 6:62; 20:17\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, an aposelba garav…®ra itima God anesiarafaz…®ma a God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo. Ez…® ghuariam me gari nagh…®n a modo.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Matyu 28:3; Mak 16:5; Luk 24:4; Jon 20:12; Aposel 10:3; 10:30\x*A ghuavanadima me kogha overiam…®n garav…®ra itima, gumazimning korotiar ghurghurimning arugha bem…®ra men m…®n tu.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Matyu 24:30; 26:64; Luk 21:27; Jon 14:3; 1 Tesalonika 1:10; 4:16; Akar Mogomem 1:7\x*Egha aning kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGalilin gumaziba, ia tizim bagha kagh tuivighav ikia p…®n overiam…®n gari? Gumazir kam Iesus, God a iniz…® a ia ategha uan Nguibam…®n ghu. Ia an ganiz…® a God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuz…® mogh…®n, kamagh…®ra a uamategham.‚Äù
\s1 Me Judas…®n ingangarir danganim bagha Matias am…®sefe
\p 
\v 12 Egha Iesus…®n aposelba Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am ategha ua Jerusalem…®n zui. Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®ar kam Jerusalem…®n borogh…®ra ikia an ruarim 1 kilomitan m…®rara ghu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Matyu 10:2-4; Mak 3:16-19; Luk 6:14-16\x*Egha me otivigha, ghuriar p…®n itir me zurara itim…®n ghuavanabo. Men ziabar kara:
\b
\pi1 Pita, Jon, Jems ko Andru, Filip ko Tomas, Bartolomyu ko Matyu, Jems, Alfius…®n otarim, ko Saimon a Selotbar gumazir mam, ko Judas, a Jems…®n otarim.
\b
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Matyu 13:55; Luk 23:49; 23:55; 24:10; Jon 6:42; 7:5\x*Egha me zurara navir vam…®ra ikia uari inigha God ko m…®gei. Ez…® amizir maba ko, Iesus…®n amebam Maria ko Iesus…®n doziba uakan.
\p 
\v 15 Dughiar kabar aven Pita n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darazir tong…®n tu. (Men av…®rim…®n d…®bobonim 120.)
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Onger Akaba 41:9\x*Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan adarasi, God…®n Duam fom…®ra Devit gamiz…®, an akar mam m…®keme. Ez…® akar kam God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven iti. Akar kam a Judas…®n m…®gei. Judas, a gumazir Iesus isa gumazir an suirazibar akazim. Akar kam dat…®r…®gh…®n Devit m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra otogha g…®fa.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Matyu 10:4; Luk 6:16; Aposel 1:25\x*Judas fom…®ra en gumazir mamra, egha uaghan ingangarir e amir kam gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Matyu 26:15; 2 Pita 2:15\x*\x - \xo 1:18-19 \xt Matyu 27:3-8\x*(Ivezir Judas uan arazir kuram…®n inizim, a nguazir mam givese. Egha nguazir kam…®n a uab…® ekunigha aremegha an m…®karzim afoaraghir…®, ez…® an muriaba bar azenim gire.
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jerusalem…®n itir darazi bar mogh…®ra bizir kam baregha, nguazir kam uan akam…®n ziar kam a gat…®, Akeldama. An m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúGhuzim…®n Nguazim.‚Äù)
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Onger Akaba 69:25; 109:8\x*Egha Pita ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Onger Akabar aven osizirir kam iti, ‚ÄòAn danganim pura ik…®, tav an danganim inian mark…®.‚Äô
\p ‚ÄúEgha a uaghan ghaze, ‚ÄòA gumazir dapanim, eght…® igharaz tav an danganim ini.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, e gumazir zurara e ko ikia uaghan Ekiam Iesus ko aruizir gumazitam am…®s…®vam.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Matyu 3:16; Mak 1:9; 16:19; Luk 3:21; 24:51; Jon 15:27; Aposel 4:33\x*Dughiar Jon gumazamiziba ruezim ko Iesus faragha ingangarim igiamra a gamir dughiam ikegha, ghua dughiar God Iesus iniz…® an e ategha ghuavanabozir dughiam…®n tu. E dughiar kaba bar e ko ikezir gumazitam am…®s…®vam. Gumazir kam Iesus…®n garima, a ua d…®kafi. An e ko m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n gun akam akunam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Egha me gumazir pumuning…®n ziamning d…®boro, Josep, an ziar mam Barsabas (an ziar igharazir mam Jastus) ko Matias.
\v 24-25 \x - \xo 1:24-25 \xt 1 Samuel 16:7; Jeremaia 11:20; Jon 2:25; Akar Mogomem 2:23\x*Egha me God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, gumazamizibar navir averiaba, n…® bar dagh fo. N…® en akagh, n…® aning…®n tav am…®seveght…®, an aposel…®n ingangarim bagh Judas…®n danganim iniam. Ingangarir kam Judas anetegha uan danganir ikiamim…®n ghu.‚Äù
\v 26 Egha me dag…®aba aning…®n ziamning osirigha torim gat…®gha aning givazvasi. Ez…® dag…®ar Matias…®n ziam is…®n itim faragha azenim gir…®. Ez…® me Matias isa, uaghan 11plan aposelbar tong…®n anet…®.
\c 2
\s1 God…®n Duam izaghiri
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt God…®n Araziba 16:9-11; Aposel 1:14\x*Ez…® Pentikos…®n Dughiar Ekiam otoz…®ma, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darasi, me bar mogh…®ra uari akuvagha danganir vam…®ran iti.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Pentikos…®n Dughiar Ekiam, an ziar igharazimra kara: Obaribar Aghavir Dughiar Ekiam.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Aposel 4:31\x*Ez…® zuam…®ra n…®g…®nir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izaghira mati am…®nir gavgavim izi. Egha d…®penir me apiaghav itim bar a giz…®vagha anevara.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Matyu 3:11\x*Egha me garima bizir mam mati avir m…®zariaba b…®aghira vaghvagha men dapanir siriabagh apiaghiri.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mak 16:17; Aposel 1:5; 4:31; 10:44-46; 1 Korin 12:10; 13:1\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam bar mogh…®ra me giz…®vagha, gavgavim me gan…®ga me gamima, me nguibar igharazibar akabav gei.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Judan gumazamizir God…®n apengan itir maba, me nguazim…®n itir kantriba bar dar ikegha izegha dat…®r…®gh…®n Jerusalem…®n iti.
\v 6 Egha me n…®g…®nir kam baregha iza bar uari akuvaghava, vaghvagha orazima gumazamiziba men nguibabar akabav gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®gavir kuram gamua okam n…®ghn…®si.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Aposel 1:11\x*Egha me d…®gavir kuram gamigha azangs…®si, ‚ÄúGumazamizir m…®geir kaba, me bar Galilin gumazamizibara!
\v 8 Ez…® manmagh…®n amiz…®, e vaghvagha me barazi me en nguibabar akabav gei?
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2 Timoti 1:15\x*En marazi Partian kantri ko Midian kantri ko Elam…®n kantribar ize. Ez…® marazi Mesopotemian Distrigh…®n ize. Ez…® marazi Judian Distrik ko Kapadosian Provins ko, Pontus…®n Provins ko, Esian Provins…®n ize.
\v 10 Ez…® marazi Frigian Distrik ko Pamfilian Provins…®n ize. Ez…® marazi Isip…®n kantri, ko Libian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibar ekiam Sairinin borogh…®n ikegha ize. Ez…® marazi Judan gumazir Rom…®n nguibam…®n ikegha izeziba. Marazi Judaba, ez…® marazi Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me Judan Arazibagh amua dar g…®n ghua, egha me uaghan, mati en marasi.
\v 11 Ez…® en marazi Krit…®n Arighat…®zim ko Arebian Distrigh…®n gumazamiziba, e vaghvagha me barazima me en nguibabar akabar God amizir bizir ekiabar gun m…®gei!‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Judan gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gamigha pura okam n…®ghn…®gha uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar bizir tizim?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Judan gumazamizir maba d…®bovir akabav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe wain…®n d…®par av…®riba amegha ongani.‚Äù
\s1 Pita akam akuri
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Pita 11plan aposelba ko tughav ikia, egha pamtem kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Judaba ko Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba, ia bar deraghv…®ra na baragh. K…® bizir otozir kam…®n gun ia m…®kemeght…®, ia a g…®fogham.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:7\x*Gumazamizir kaba wain…®n d…®pam…®n onganizir puvat…®. Ia fo, kar 9 klogh…®n m…®zarazimra.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Judaba dughiar kam…®n m…®zaraghara d…®par onganiba apir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n Pita akar kam me m…®gei.\f*
\v 16 Bizir otozir kam, kar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Joel fom…®ra m…®kemez…® mogh…®n:
\b
\q1 
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17-21 \xt Joel 2:28-32; Sekaraia 12:10; Jon 7:38; Aposel 10:45; 21:9\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòGod kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\q2 Dughiar g…®n izamibar k…® uan Duam gumazamiziba bar me gingegham.
\q1 Eght…® ian otariba ko guiviba God…®n akam inigha izir gumazamizibar m…®n m…®k…®mt…®ma,
\q2 ian gumazir igiaba irebabar m…®n bizibar gant…®,
\q3 ian gumazir ghuriba irebabar ganam.
\q1 
\v 18 Dughiar kabar k…® uaghan uan Duam is…®,
\q2 uan ingangarir gumaziba ko ingangarir amizibagh ingegham,
\q3 eght…® me God…®n akam inigha izir gumazamizibar akabav k…®mam.
\q1 
\v 19 Eght…® k…® p…®n overiam…®n d…®gavir kuram gamir araziba akakagh,
\q2 egh nguazim…®n mirakel…®n arazibar amuam.
\q3 Eght…® ghuzim ko avim ko m…®turir dafam otogham.
\q1 
\v 20 Eght…® aruem m…®tarmeght…®, iak…®nim ghuzim…®n m…®n otogham.
\q2 Bizir kaba faragh otivight…®,
\q3 g…®n Ekiam Izamin Dughiam otogham.
\q2 Dughiar kam…®n Ekiam uan gavgavim ko angazangarim sara izam.
\q1 
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Rom 10:13\x*Eght…® Ekiam…®n ziam…®n d…®mamin adarasi,
\q2 a men akurvagham.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Jon 3:2; 14:10-11; Hibru 2:4\x*‚ÄúIsrael…®n gumazamiziba, ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baragh. Nasaret…®n Iesus, God ia bagha anemadagha gavgavim a gan…®ngiz…®, a ian tong…®n ingangarir gavgavir ekiaba ko mirakel…®n gavgavibagh amiz…®, da otiviz…® ia dar ganigha uari fo.
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Matyu 27:35; Mak 15:24; Luk 23:33; Jon 19:18; Aposel 4:28; 1 Pita 1:20\x*God uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua ia bagha fom…®ra n…®ghn…®zir mam gamigha, uan Otarim isa ian agharim gat…®. Ez…® ia gumazir kurabar agharim…®n, a isa ter ighuvim…®n a gafuz…®, an areme.
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Matyu 28:5-6; Mak 16:6; Luk 24:5; Aposel 3:15; 4:10; 10:40; 13:30-31; 17:31; 1 Korin 15:15\x*Ovevem bar Iesus…®n suiraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n, God a gamiz…® a d…®kavigha ovevem…®n gavgavim ataki.
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25-28 \xt Onger Akaba 16:8-11\x*Devit…®n Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme:
\b
\q1 ‚Äú ‚ÄòK…® Ekiam…®n garima a zurara bar nan borogh…®ra iti.
\q2 A bar rogh…®ra ikia gavgavim na gan…®di.
\q3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® atiatiava agoir puvat…®.
\q1 
\v 26-27 \x - \xo 2:26-27 \xt Aposel 13:35\x*N…® na ateght…®,
\q2 k…® Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n ikian kogham.
\q1 N…® ua bagha inabazir gumazim aneteght…®ma,
\q2 an inivaf…®zim kurighan kogham.
\q1 Kamagh…®n nan navir averiam bar akonge.
\q2 Ez…® k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibagh ami.
\q1 God na damuamin bizir aghuiba,
\q2 k…® da bagha m…®zuai.
\q1 
\v 28 Ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniamin tuavim,
\q2 n…® nan akagha g…®fa.
\q1 N…® na ateght…® k…® n…® ko ikiam,
\q2 egh n…® na damut…®,
\q3 k…® bar akuegham.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 2:29 \xt 1 Atriviba 2:10; Aposel 13:36; 2 Timoti 2:8\x*‚ÄúNan adarasi, k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, en ovavim Devit aremez…® me anefa. Ez…® an dag…®ar mozim dat…®r…®gh…®n e ko ikia kati.
\v 30 \x - \xo 2:30 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12-13; Onger Akaba 89:3-4; 132:11\x*Devit a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, egha a fo, God m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim a gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄòN…®n atrivir danganim…®n k…® n…®n ovavitam afagham.‚Äô
\v 31 \x - \xo 2:31 \xt Onger Akaba 16:10; Aposel 13:35\x*God g…®n damuamin bizim, Devit a g…®fo, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim, Krais, an aremegh ua d…®kavamin bizim m…®gei. Egha ghaze, God aneteght…®ma a Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n ikian kogham. Egh an inivaf…®zim kurighan kogham.\f + \fr 2:31 \ft Grigh…®n akam me ghaze, ‚ÄúKrais,‚Äù an m…®ngarim God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.\f*
\v 32 \x - \xo 2:32 \xt Aposel 1:8; 2:24\x*Ez…® gumazir kam Iesus, God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi. Ez…® e uari uan damazibar an ganigha, an gun m…®gei.
\v 33 \x - \xo 2:33 \xt Jon 14:26; Aposel 1:4; 5:31; 7:55-56; 10:45; Hibru 10:12\x*Ez…® Iesus ghuanabogha uan Afeziam God…®n agharir guvim gaperaghav ikia a da gavgavim isi. Ez…® an Afeziam a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n uan Duam Iesus gan…®ngi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia oragha garir bizir kaba, Iesus uab…® dagh ami.
\v 34 \x - \xo 2:34-35 \xt Onger Akaba 110:1\x*Devit Iesus…®n m…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuzir puvat…®. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei:
\b
