\v 36 \x - \xo 2:36 \xt Aposel 5:30-31\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia ia bar bizir kam g…®fo, ia m…®suegha ter ighuvim…®n gurazir Iesus…®n kam, God dat…®r…®gh…®n a gamiz…® an Ekiam…®n oto, a Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazamizir av…®riba uan naviba iragha rue
