\v 37 \x - \xo 2:37 \xt Sekaraia 12:10; Luk 3:10-12; Aposel 9:6; 16:30\x*Gumazamiziba Pitan akaba barazima, da men navibagh kuiz…®, me kamagh…®n Pita ko aposel…®n igharazibav gei, ‚ÄúEn aveghbuaba, e manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù
