\v 38 \x - \xo 2:38 \xt Luk 24:47; Aposel 3:19\x*Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar navibagh iragh Krais Iesus…®n ziam…®n rueght…®, a ian arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®t…®, God uan Duam ia dan…®ngam.
\v 39 \x - \xo 2:39 \xt Aisaia 57:19; Joel 2:28; Aposel 10:45; 14:27; Efesus 2:13; 2:17\x*God fom…®ra akam ak…®righa ghaze, a uan Duam is…®, ia ko, ian boriba ko, ian saghon itir darazi bar, a uan Duam ia dan…®ngam. God, en Ekiam, gumazamizir a diaziba, a uan Duam me dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 40 \x - \xo 2:40 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:5; Filipai 2:15\x*Egha Pita m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar me gamua akar gavgavir maba sara me m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa uari uarir akuragh, eght…® God dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir kurar kabagh as…®ghas…®gh uaghan ia gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 41 \x - \xo 2:41 \xt Aposel 2:47; 4:4; 5:14\x*Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba an akam baregha a gifuegha, egha rue. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n God ua 3,000plan gumazamizir maba ua me iniz…®, me Krais…®n adarazir aven ize.
\s1 God…®n gumazamizibar ik…®r…®m…®rim
\p 
\v 42 \x - \xo 2:42 \xt Aposel 20:7\x*Krais…®n adarazi me aposelbar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragha, bizibar uarir akurvagha, uari isava apava, God ko m…®k…®masa bar ifonge.\f + \fr 2:42 \ft Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Faragha zuir Krais…®n adarazi uari akuva egha uari koma api. Me amegha g…®vagha, me Iesus…®n inivaf…®zim ko ghuzim g…®n…®ghn…®gha bret ko wain…®n d…®pam api.\f*
\v 43 \x - \xo 2:43 \xt Mak 16:17; Aposel 4:33; 5:11-12\x*Ez…® aposelba d…®gavir kuram gamir arazir av…®riba ko mirakel…®n av…®ribagh ami. Kamagh…®n gumazamizir av…®riba d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 44 \x - \xo 2:44 \xt Aposel 4:32-35; 5:12; 6:8\x*Egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darasi, navir vam…®ra ikiava, bizir me itiba, me uarir akurvasi.
\v 45 Egha me uan nguaziba ko biziba amaga dar dag…®aba isava, dagheba otevezibar akurvasi.
\v 46 \x - \xo 2:46 \xt Luk 24:53; Aposel 1:14; 20:7\x*Dughiabar zurara, me God…®n D…®penir av…®zim…®n uari akufi. Egha d…®peniba roa vaghvagha dagh arua, uari isava apava, bar akongegha, men naviba bar dera.
\v 47 \x - \xo 2:47 \xt Aposel 2:41; 4:33; 5:14; 6:7; 11:21; 11:24; Rom 14:18\x*Egha me God…®n ziam fema, gumazamizir igharaziba me bagha bar akonge. Ez…® Ekiam dughiabar zurara gumazamiziba akurvaghav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men d…®bobonim dughiabar ghuavanagav…®ra iti.
\c 3
\s1 Gumazir suer kurar mam ua dera
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Aposel 2:42; 10:9; 10:30\x*Aruer mam, aruem 3 klogh…®n tu, kar Judaba God ko m…®geir dughiam. Dughiar kamra Pita ko Jon God…®n D…®penim…®n zui.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Jon 9:1; Aposel 14:8\x*Ez…® gumazir navim…®n averara suemning ikuvizir mam iti. Ez…® gumaziba anetera ghua God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akar mam…®n aner…®si, an ziam, Tiar Akar Bar Dirim. A kagh ikiava dag…®aba bagha gumazamizir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven zuibagh ginge.
\v 3 Ez…® a gari Pita ko Jon God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mangasa izima a dag…®aba bagha aning ginge.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Aposel 14:9\x*Ez…® Pita bar anar…®ra gari, ez…® Jon uakan. Egha Pita ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kagh gan ganigh!‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® gumazim bizitam iniasa n…®ghn…®gha, aningra gari.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Aposel 3:16; 4:10\x*Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dag…®aba puvat…®, bizir k…® itim, k…® n…® dan…®ngasa. Nasaret…®n gumazim Krais Iesus, an ziam…®n, n…® d…®kavigh daru!‚Äù
\v 7 Egha Pita an dafarir guvim…®n suiragha a fe. Ez…® an duiavaniba ko dagariba zuam…®ra gavgafi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Aisaia 35:6; Jon 5:14; Aposel 14:10\x*Ez…® a d…®kavigha uab…® ekunigha magh…®ram arui. Egha a Pita ko Jon sara God…®n D…®penir av…®zibar aven aruava, p…®n uab…® ekura, God…®n ziam fe.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Aposel 4:16; 4:21\x*Ez…® gumazamiziba bar an gari an arua God…®n ziam fema,
\v 10 me an ganigha a g…®fogha ghaze, gumazir kamra God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akar ziam, Tiar Akar Bar Dirim…®n apiav ikia, dag…®aba bagha gumazamizibagh inge. Egha me d…®gavir kuram gamigha pura n…®ghn…®si, manmagh…®n amizir bizim kav bato.
\s1 Pita God…®n D…®penim…®n aven // akam akuri
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® gumazamiziba akar kam baregha, d…®gavir kuram gamigha, ivemara ghua gumazir kam…®n garima a Pita ko Jon…®n suiragha, God…®n D…®penir azuarim…®n tughav iti. D…®penir azuarir kam…®n ziam, Solomon…®n Azuarim.
\v 12 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n ganigha, me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsrael…®n gumazamiziba, tizim bagha bizir kam ia gamiz…®ma ia d…®gavir kuram gami? Ia tizim bagha pamtem gan gara ghaze, ga ti uan gavgavibar tuavim, o ga God…®n damazim…®n derav…®ra itir tuavim…®n, gumazir kam gamiz…®ma an arui? Bar puvat…®.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 3:6; 3:15; Matyu 22:32; Luk 23:13-25; Aposel 2:23; 7:32\x*Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God, a en inazir afeziabar God, a uan ingangarir gumazim Iesus bar a p…®rafa. Ia, an aremeghasa a isa apanibar dafarim gat…®. Egha dughiar Pailat anetagh…®raghasa m…®geim, ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòE tong a gifongezir puvat…®!‚Äô Egha ak…®rim a gasara.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Matyu 27:15-23; Mak 15:6-14; Luk 23:13-23; Jon 19:12-15\x*Ia God…®n damazim…®n zuegha derazir gumazim…®n aghuaghava, gumazir kuram uari bagh anetagh…®raghasa Pailat m…®gei. A gumazibav sozi me ariaghirezir gumazim.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Aposel 1:8; 2:24; 2:32; 2:36; 4:10\x*Ia gamiz…® ia angam…®ra itir gumazim, ia a m…®soghez…® an aremez…® God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi. Ga uaning bizir kam…®n ganighava a g…®fogha an gun m…®gei.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Matyu 9:22; Aposel 4:10; 14:9\x*Ga Iesus…®n ziam…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Ez…® Iesus…®n ziam…®n gumazir ia ganigha fozir kam, a gavgavim ini. Iesusra gan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam gamiz…®, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kamra gumazir kam gamiz…®, a bar deraz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n uari an gari.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Luk 23:34; Jon 16:3; 1 Korin 2:8; 1 Timoti 1:13\x*‚ÄúEz…® nan adarasi, k…® kamagh…®n fo, ia uan gumazir dapaniba ko amizir arazim, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Aisaia 50:6; 53:5; Luk 24:27; 24:44; Aposel 26:22; 1 Pita 1:10-11\x*Ez…® God fom…®ra an akam inigha izir gumaziba bar me m…®kemez…®, me m…®g…®a ghaze, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, Krais, m…®zazim iniam. Ez…® God uan m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh amiz…® mogh…®n dar dagheba otifi.
\p 
\v 19-20 \x - \xo 3:19-20 \xt Aposel 2:38\x*‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n ifueght…®ma, God ian arazir kuraba angaright…® dughiar kabar God…®n Duam iz…®va ian duaba avughs…®zim ko navir am…®rizim, ia danight…®, God ia bagh Iesus uam anemangam, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim, a ia bagha anem…®sefe. Ia bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh da inis…®, uan navibagh iragh…®va uamategh God bagh iz…®.
\v 21 God fom…®ra uan akam inigha izir gumazir zuezibav kemez…®, me ghaze, ‚ÄòIesus dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n Nguibam ik…®, mang…® dughiar God bizibar amut…® da bar igiabar otivam.‚Äô Eght…® God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, biziba bar otivam.
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:15-19; Aposel 7:37\x*Ez…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam God fom…®ra Moses m…®kemez…®, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam ian God, a nan m…®n ia bagh akam inigha izir gumazitam, ian tong…®n gumazitamra m…®sevegham. Bizir a m…®geiba, ia da baragh dar amu.
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Ofa Gami 23:29\x*A barazir puvat…®ziba God me gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® me ua God…®n adarazi ko ikian kogham.‚Äô\f + \fr 3:23 \ft Akar kam, akam inigha izir gumazir God amadazim, a God…®n Araziba 18:15, 16, 17, 18, 19…®n iti. Pita kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Iesus, a uab…® akam inigha izir gumazim.\f*
\v 24 God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba bar, Samuel…®n tugha izi, me bar m…®g…®a dughiar kabar gun m…®keme.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Jenesis 12:3; 18:18; 22:18; Rom 9:4; 9:8; Galesia 3:8; 3:26\x*‚ÄúGod fom…®ra uan akam inigha izir gumaziba Akar Gavgavim me gan…®ngi, ez…® ia men boriba m…®n ik…®, eght…® Akar Gavgavir kabanang uaghan iana. God fom…®ra Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim ian ovaviba ko a gamiz…®, ia men boribar m…®n iti, ez…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, a uaghan iana. God kamagh…®n Abraham m…®keme, ‚ÄòK…® kamagh…®n damuam, n…®n ovavibar borim…®n tuavim…®n, k…® nguazir kam…®n itir nguibaba bar derav…®ra me damuam.‚Äô
\v 26 \x - \xo 3:26 \xt Matyu 10:5; Luk 24:47; Aposel 13:32-33; 13:46\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, ia vaghvagh uan arazir kuraba ateght…®, a derav…®ra ia damuam. Bizir kam bagha a uan ingangarir gumazim am…®sevegha ia bagha faragha anemada.‚Äù
\c 4
\s1 Pita ko Jon Judan kot…®n iti
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Luk 22:4; 22:52\x*Pita ko Jon gumazamizibav g…®av…®ra itima, ofa gamir gumaziba ko God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazibar gumazir dapanim ko Sadyusiba, me izava aning bato.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazibar ekiam, a ofa gamir gumazir mam. A Livain gumaziba, a me gativagha men garima, me God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n ingara bizibar gara polisman…®n ingangarim gami.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Matyu 22:23; Aposel 23:8\x*Egha me fo, Pita ko Jon Iesus aremegha ua d…®kavizir bizir kam…®n gun gumazamizibav gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir dapanibar naviba aning bagha bar ikufi.
\v 3 Egha me Pita ko Jon…®n agharimning suiragha aning kot dar…®ghasava amima, am…®nim p…®ri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me aning sel gat…®z…® aning ikia ghua am…®mzaraghan.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Aposel 2:41\x*Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba akar kam baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n an iti. Egha Krais…®n adarazir d…®bobonim bar ekevegha ghua 5,000…®n borogh…®n tu.
\s1 Me Pita ko Jon kot gat…®
\p 
\v 5 Egha am…®mzaraghan Judan gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar gumazir aruaba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me Jerusalem…®n uari akuvagha iti.\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Gumazir okoruar pumuning ko m…®kezim, me uari akufa. Egha me Judabar Kaunselbar m…®n iti. Egha men ingangarim kamak…®n, me Judabar dabirabim gativagha egha men gari.\f*
\v 6 Anas, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, a uaghan iti, ez…® Kaiafas ko Jon ko Aleksanda ko ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n adarazir gumazir igharaziba, me uaghan iti.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Matyu 21:23; Aposel 7:27\x*Egha me m…®kemez…®, gumaziba Pita ko Jon inigha men damazibar izez…®, me magh…®ram aning…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄúGua gavgavir manam inigha, tinan ziam…®n gua bizir kabagh ami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Matyu 10:19-20\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam Pita giz…®vaz…®ma, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judan gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar gumazir aruaba!
\v 9 Ia ti gumazir suer kurar ga akurazir kam bagha gan azangs…®gh, egha ti uaghan foghasa, gumazir kam a manmagh…®n dera.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Aposel 2:24; 3:6; 3:13-16\x*Eght…® ia ko Israel…®n itir darasi, ia bar mogh…®ra bizir kam g…®fogh! Kar Nasaret…®n gumazim Krais Iesus…®n ziam…®n, gumazir ian damazibar tughav itir kam ua dera. Gumazir kam a Iesus, ia a inigha ter ighuvim gafuz…®, an aremez…® God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi.\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Gumazir okoruar kam, Judabar Kaunselba, merara Pailat (Rom…®n gavman faragha zuir gumazim) m…®g…®a ghaze, a Iesus m…®sueght…® an ovengegh. N…® Luk 22:66--23:5…®n gan. Egha Iesus ovengegha g…®vaz…®, me gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n an ikian me aghua.\f*
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Onger Akaba 118:22; Aisaia 28:16; Matyu 21:42\x*Ez…® Iesus:
\b
\q1 ‚Äú ‚ÄòKar d…®penir ak…®nir ingangarir gumaziba aghuazim,
\q2 a dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®penim aterir guarim gava.‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Matyu 1:21; Aposel 10:43\x*‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazitam en akuraghan kogham, bar puvat…®. Iesus…®n ziamra e akurvazir aghuim iniam. A uab…®ra, en Akurvazir Gumazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Egha me Pita ko Jon…®n garima aning bar gavgavighav atiatir puvat…®gha me m…®geima, me aning…®n ganighava fo, aning sure gamizir puvat…®. Aning pura gumazir k…®nimning. Egha me aning…®n gara d…®gavir kuram gamigha ghaze, gumazir kamning Iesus koma arui.
\v 14 Egha me gumazir faragha suer ikuvizim…®n gari, a Jon ko Pita, ko tughav itima, me bizitam m…®k…®man asa.
\p 
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me akar gavgavimra aning gan…®ngiz…®ma, aning Judan kot…®n d…®penim ategha zuima, me aning bagha akam m…®sosi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Jon 11:47; Aposel 3:9-10\x*Egha me uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúE manmagh…®n gumazir kamning damuam? Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba, fo, aning mirakel…®n bar ekiam gami. Eght…® e kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, bizir kam guizbang…®ra otozir puvat…®.
\v 17 E kamagh…®n aghua, gumazamizir igharaziba bizir kam baraghan kogham. Egh e akar bar gavgavimra aning danight…®, aning ua Iesus…®n ziam…®n gun bar tav m…®k…®man kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Aposel 5:28; 5:40\x*Egha me ua aning…®n diaz…®ma aning aven ghuz…®, me akar gavgavim…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, gua uamategh Iesus…®n ziam…®n gun m…®k…®m…®va gumazitabar sure damuan bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 19-20 \x - \xo 4:19-20 \xt Aposel 5:29\x*\x - \xo 4:19-20 \xt Aposel 1:8; 22:15; 1 Jon 1:1-3\x*Ez…® Pita ko Jon men akam ikaragha m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning ganighava oraghizir bizibar ghuangs…®ghan kogham, ga dar gun m…®k…®mv…®ra ikiam. Ia uari n…®ghn…®gh, arazir manam God…®n damazim…®n dera, ga God…®n akam baragham, o ga ian akam baragham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 21-22 Gumazir Pita ko Jon God…®n gavgavim…®n amizir derazim, a 40plan azenibagh afira. Gumazamiziba uari bizir kabar gari da otiviz…®, kamagh…®n me God…®n ziam fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir dapaniba ivezir kuram aning dan…®ngasa pura n…®ghn…®si, me manmagh…®n aning damuam. Egha me atiatir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavir maba uam aning gamigha aning amadaz…® aning zui.
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darazi God ko m…®gei
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Judan kot…®n aven itir gumaziba Pita ko Jon ataghiz…®ma aning azenim gir…®gha uamategha uan adarazi bagha ghu. Egha aning ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar gumazir aruaba aning m…®kemezir akabar gun uan adarazi bar me m…®keme.
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:11; Nehemia 9:6; Onger Akaba 146:6\x*Ez…® me kamagh…®n oregha uari akuvagha God ko m…®gei. Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn Ekiar en garim, n…® overiam ko nguazim…®n ingarigha, ongarim sara ingari, egha dar itir biziba sara, bar dar ingari.
\v 25 \x - \xo 4:25-26 \xt Onger Akaba 2:1-2\x*Fom…®ra n…®n Duam akar mam en ovavim Devit, a n…®n ingangarir gumazim, n…® akar kam a gan…®ngi. Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n m…®keme:
\b
\q1 ‚Äú ‚ÄòEz…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba tizim bagha atari?
\q2 Egha me tizim bagha arazir kurabar amuasava akabav sosi?
\q1 
\v 26 Ez…® nguazir kam…®n itir atriviba me m…®soghasava ami.
\q2 Ez…® gumazir ekiaba uari inigha Ekiam m…®soghasa.
\q3 Egha uaghan God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim m…®soghasa.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Matyu 27:1-2; Mak 15:1; Luk 23:1; 23:7-11; Jon 18:28-29; Aposel 3:13\x*‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Herot ko Pontius Pailat, Israel…®n gumaziba, ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba sara, me Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n uari akuvagha arazir kurabar God…®n ingangarir gumazir zuezim, Iesus damuasava akabav sosi. A gumazir n…® fom…®ra uan ingangarim bagha inabazim.
\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt Aposel 2:23; 3:18\x*N…® fom…®ram otivasa m…®kemezir biziba, me n…®n gavgavim ko n…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghua dagh ami.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Aposel 9:27; 13:46; 19:8; Efesus 6:19\x*Ez…® Ekiam, n…® atiatir akar me e gan…®ngizibagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh n…® en akuraght…®ma e tugh gavgavigh atiatingan kogh n…®n akam akunam.
\v 30 Egh n…® uan dafarim ar…®mariar gumazamizibar ar…®ght…® me ghuamagham. Egh n…® mirakelba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar amut…® da Iesus…®n ziam…®n otivam, a n…®n ingangarir gumazir bar zuezim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Aposel 2:4; 4:29; 16:26\x*Egha me Afeziam ko m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, danganir me itim ivazvazima, God…®n Duam bar mogh…®ra me giz…®vaz…®, me atiatir puvat…®gha God…®n akam akuri.
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darazi uan bizibar uarir akurvasi
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 4:32 \xt Aposel 2:44-45; 2 Korin 13:11; 1 Pita 3:8\x*Egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darasi, me bar navir vam…®ra ko n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra iti. Men tav uab…®ra uan bizitam gamir puvat…®, me uari inighava biziba bar mogh…®ra dagh ami.
\v 33 \x - \xo 4:33 \xt Aposel 1:8; 1:22; 2:45-47\x*Egha aposelba God…®n gavgavir ekiam…®n amodogh…®n, Ekiam Iesus aremegha ua d…®kavizir bizir kam…®n gun gumazamizibav gei. Ez…® God…®n apangkuvir ekiamra me ko iti.
\v 34-35 \x - \xo 4:34-35 \xt Aposel 2:45\x*Ez…® kamagh…®n, men tav bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir nguaziba ko d…®peniba itiba, me da amaga dar dag…®aba inigha iza aposelbagh an…®dima, me da isava gumazamizir biziba puvat…®zibar akurvasi.
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 4:36 \xt Aposel 11:22-26; 13:2-3\x*Gumazir mam Josep, a Livain gumazim. Ez…® aposelba Barnabas a gar…®si. An m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, gumazamizibar akurvagha gavgavim me gan…®dir gumazim. Barnabas, a Saiprus…®n Arighat…®zim…®n gumazim.
\v 37 A uan nguazir mam amadagha, an dag…®aba inigha aposelbagh an…®ngi.
\c 5
\s1 Ananaias ko Safaira God gifari
\p 
\v 1 Gumazir mam Ananaias, an amuim Safaira, aning uaghara fuegha uan nguazir mam amadagha an ivezim ini.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Aposel 4:34-37\x*Egha aning uaghara bar fogha, Ananaias dag…®ar maba ua bagha dar suira. Egha naba inigha aposelbagh ifaragha me gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt God…®n Araziba 23:21\x*Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n Ananaias m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua, Satan ataghiz…®ma a n…®n navim giz…®vaz…®, n…® God…®n Duam gifari? Egha nguazir ivezim…®n dag…®ar maba n…® ua bagha dar suira?
\v 4 Kar n…®n nguazim, n…® uab…® ifuegha anemada. An ivezim…®n dag…®aba uaghan n…®n dag…®abara. N…® manmagh…®n n…®ghnigha uan dag…®ar kabar e gifari? N…® gumazamizibagh ifari puvat…®, n…® God gifari.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Ananaias kamagh…®n oregha degiaghir…®gha magh…®ram areme. Ez…® gumazamiziba bizir kam baregha atiatir ekiam me ini.
\v 6 Ez…® gumazir igiaba izava an kuam nomkegha a inigha azenan ghuava a mozim gat…®.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® auan pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaz…®, an amuim fozir puvat…®gha aven izi.
\v 8 Ez…® Pita an azara, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®k…®m, kar nguazir ivezim, n…® Ananaias ko gua a ini?‚Äù
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, bar an ivezimra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua manmaghsua v…®rara fuegha God…®n Duam gifari? N…® gan! Gumazir n…®n pam mozim gat…®ziba, me tiar akam…®n iti. Egh me uaghan n…®n kuam inigh azenan mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Pita m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Safaira magh…®ram an suemning…®n ir…®ghava areme. Ez…® gumazir igiaba aven iza garima an aremez…® me a inigha azenan ghugha an pam…®n mozim…®n m…®riam…®n anefa.
\v 11 Ez…® atiatir ekiam Krais…®n adarazi bar me batoz…®, gumazir bizir kaba baraghiziba bar uaghan bar atiatingi.
\s1 Mirakel…®n av…®rav…®riba otifi
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Aposel 2:43; 14:3; Rom 15:19; 2 Korin 12:12\x*Aposelba mirakel…®n av…®riba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir bizir av…®riba, gumazamizibar tong…®n dagh ami. Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir gumazamiziba, me Solomon…®n Azuarim…®n zurara uari akufi.
\v 13 Gumazir igharaziba, me ko poghasa tong n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Me men ziaba fa egha fo, me arazir aghuim gami.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Aposel 2:41; 21:20\x*Marazi me ko poghan aghua, ez…® av…®rim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n ikia men aven zuima, men d…®bobonim bar ghuavanabo.
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Matyu 9:21; 14:36; Aposel 19:12\x*Kamagh…®n, gumaziba ar…®mariar gumazamiziba inigha men m…®siaba ko akuriaba sara me atera iza tuavir m…®riam…®n me ar…®si. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, Pitan nedazim me gis…®n mang…®t…® me ua ghuamagham.\f + \fr 5:15 \ft Gumazamizir kaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n iti, aruem Pita gisiraght…® an nedazim ar…®mariar gumazamizibagh is…®n ik…®t…®, me ua deragham.\f*
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Mak 6:56; Aposel 19:11-12\x*Ez…® uaghan Jerusalem torim gat…®zir nguibar dozibar gumazir av…®rim, me uan ar…®mariar gumazamiziba inigha ize. Egha uaghan uan gumazamizir duar kuraba apazaziba inigha izez…®ma, me bar mogh…®ra ghuamaghegha dera.
\s1 Ensel aposelbar akuraz…®, // me kalabus ataki
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Aposel 4:1-2; 4:6\x*Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ko an akurvazir adarasi, kar Sadyusibar aven itir gumaziba. Me aposelba amir biziba bagha navim ikufi.
\v 18 Egha Sadyusiba men suiragha kalabuziar ekiam gat…®.
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Aposel 12:7-10; 16:26\x*Me kalabus…®n itima, d…®mangan Ekiam…®n ensel tiaba kuigha me inigha azenan ize.
\v 20 Egha ensel kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n av…®zibar tuiv ik…®r…®m…®rir igiar kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar, gumazamizibav k…®m.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® am…®nim itima aposelba, ensel me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n aven ghua, gumazamizibar sure gami.
\p Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim uan akurvaziba ko iza, Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazibar diaz…®, me ghua uari akufa. Israel…®n gumazir aruaba bar uari akufa. Egha me kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n aposelba inigh izasa akam amada.
\v 22 Ez…® polis…®n maba ghua kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n otogha garima, me itir puvat…®, ez…® me uamategha iza bizir kam…®n gun m…®gei,
\v 23 ‚ÄúE kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n garima me derav…®ra an tiam asaraz…® kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumaziba an tiar akam…®n tuivighav iti. Ez…® e tiaba kuigha garima, tav aven itir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® me ghua bizir kam…®n gun m…®kemez…®, God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazibar dapanim ko ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba pura n…®ghn…®si, bizir tizitam uam otogham?\f + \fr 5:24 \ft Grigh…®n akam, vez…®n kam…®n deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®. Gumazir maba akar kam giragha ghaze, ‚ÄúMe n…®ghn…®gha egha ghaze, bizir tizim dat…®r…®gh…®n otogham?‚Äù\f*
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® gumazir mam iza ghaze, ‚ÄúIa oragh! Gumazir ia kalabus gat…®ziba God…®n D…®penir m…®riam…®n tughav ikia gumazamizibar sure gami.‚Äù
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Matyu 14:5; 21:26\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazibar gumazir dapanim, uan gumazir a ko ingariba ko ghua aposelba inigha izi. Me kamagh…®n atiati, gumazamiziba dag…®abar me ginivigham, egha me pura n…®m…®ra me inigha izi.
\s1 Aposelba Judan kot…®n aven itir gumaziba akam me m…®k…®man atiatir puvat…®
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumaziba, me aposelba inigha izegha me m…®geima, me Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazibar damazim…®n tuifi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim me kot…®n Itir bizim bagha men azangs…®si.
\v 28 \x - \xo 5:28 \xt Matyu 27:25; Aposel 2:23; 2:36; 4:18; 7:52\x*Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE akar gavgavim ia gan…®ga ghaze, ia Iesus…®n ziam…®n gumazamizibar sure damuan mark…®! Ez…® ia orazir puvat…®gha men sure gamima ian suren m…®g…®r…®g…®aba Jerusalem bar a garui. Egha ia ghaze, e Iesus m…®soghez…® an areme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 5:29 \xt Aposel 4:19\x*Ez…® Pita aposel…®n igharaziba ko, me kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE God baragham, e gumazamiziba baraghan kogham.
\v 30 \x - \xo 5:30 \xt Aposel 3:15; 10:39; 13:29; Galesia 3:13; 1 Pita 2:24\x*Iarara Iesus…®n m…®suegha ter ighuvim…®n aneguraz…®ma an areme. Ez…® en ovavibar God Iesus fez…® a ua d…®kafi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 5:31 \xt Aposel 2:33-34; 3:15; Efesus 1:20; Filipai 2:9; Hibru 2:10; 12:2\x*Ez…® God a isa uan agharir guvim…®n anet…®z…®, an Atrivim…®n Otarim ko Gumazamizibar Akurvaghamin Gumazim…®n ikiam. Egh a Israelia damut…® me navibagh iraght…®, God men arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.
\v 32 \x - \xo 5:32 \xt Jon 15:26-27; Aposel 1:8; 2:4; 10:44\x*E God amizir bizir kaba uan damazibar dar ganigha dar gun m…®gei. Ez…® God…®n Duam uaghan bizir kabar gun m…®gei. God baragha an g…®n zui adarasi, a uan Duam me gan…®ngi.‚Äù
\s1 Gamaliel…®n fofozim
\p 
\v 33 \x - \xo 5:33 \xt Aposel 7:54\x*Judan kot…®n aven itir gumaziba kamagh…®n aposelbar akam baregha, men naviba me bagha bar ikufi. Egha me m…®sueght…® me aremeghasa n…®ghn…®si.
\v 34 Ez…® Farisin gumazir mam Gamaliel, Judan Arazibar sure gamizir gumazir me bar ifongezim. A Judan kot…®n aven tugha ghaze, aposelba tong azenan ikegh.\f + \fr 5:34 \ft Dughiar Pol t…®ghar Krais…®n adarazir mav…®n otivam, gumazir kam Gamaliel an sure gami. N…® akar Aposel 22:3…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 35 Egha a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabagh ami, ‚ÄúIsrael…®n gumaziba, ia arazitam gumazir kabar amus…® derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 36 \x - \xo 5:36 \xt Aposel 21:38\x*Bogh…®mra Teudas otogha kamagh…®n uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® gumazir dapanir mam, ez…® 400…®n borogh…®ra ghuzir gumaziba an g…®n ghue. Ez…® gavman a m…®soghez…®, an areme. Ez…® an g…®n zuir darazi bar uari aghams…®ki. Ez…® me amizir bizir kam dagheba puvat…®.
\v 37 Ez…® an g…®n, gavman gumazamiziba d…®borir dughiam, Galilin gumazir mam Judas oto. Egha, a gumazir b…®zir mam…®n faragha ghuava me gavman ko m…®sosi. A uaghan aremez…® an g…®n zuir darasi, me uari aghams…®ki.
\v 38 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa. Ia bizitam…®n gumazir kabar amuan mark…®! Me ateght…® me mar mang…®! Ia pura gan, men ingangarim gumazitam gis…®n tugh…®va, degeghir…®gham.
\v 39 \x - \xo 5:39 \xt Luk 21:15; Aposel 7:51; 9:5; 1 Korin 1:25\x*Egh me God…®n tugh bizim damut…®, ia men anogoroghan kogham. Ia fogh suam, ia God ko m…®sosi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 40 \x - \xo 5:40 \xt Aposel 4:18\x*Ez…® me Gamaliel…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghugha aposelbar diaz…®, me aven ghuez…® me pura me fozoroke. Egha Iesus…®n ziam…®n bizibav k…®man men anogoregha me ataghiz…® me ghue.
\p 
\v 41 \x - \xo 5:41 \xt Matyu 5:10-12; 1 Pita 4:13\x*Egha me ghaze, God e bagha bar akongegha en amamangat…®z…®, e Iesus…®n ziam…®n os…®mt…®ziba ini. Egha kamagh…®n me Judan kot…®n aven itir gumaziba atagh…®ragha bar akonge.
\v 42 \x - \xo 5:42 \xt Aposel 9:22; 17:3\x*Egha dughiaba zurara me God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riaba ko d…®penibar Akar Aghuim gumazamiziba sure gamuav…®ra iti. Egha akam me m…®k…®ra ghaze, Iesus a Krais, God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.
\c 6
\s1 Me 7pla gumazir maba aposelbar akurvaghasa me am…®sefe
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Aposel 2:41; 4:35; 5:14; 9:29\x*Dughiar kabar Iesus…®n suren gumazamizibar d…®bobonim bar ghuavanadi. Ez…® suren gumazamizir maba Grigh…®n akam…®n m…®gei, ez…® marazi Aram…®n akam m…®gei. Ez…® Grighba ghaze, ‚ÄúDughiar av…®riba ia zurara gumazamizir dagheba puvat…®zibar akurvasi, egha ia en amuir odiaribar akurvazir puvat…®.‚Äù Bizir kam bagha me uarir atari.\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Aram…®n akam, a Judia ko Galilin Distrigh…®n gumazibar akam. A Hibrun akam…®n m…®n ghu.\f*
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® aposel…®n 12pla, suren gumazamiziba bar men diaz…® me iza uari akuvaz…®ma, me kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE God…®n akam akurir ingangarim ategh…®va dagher ingangarim damuam, kamagh…®n derazir puvat…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:13; Aposel 16:2; 1 Timoti 3:7\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, en adarasi, ia uarir tong…®n 7plan gumaziba m…®sefegh. Men araziba gumazamizibar damazibar bar deragh, God…®n Duam me giz…®vaght…®, me uaghan fofozir aghuarim ik…®. Eght…® e me is…® ingangarir kam dat…®ght…®, me an ganam.
\v 4 Eght…® e uari ingangarir kamning damuam, e God ko m…®k…®m…®va, God…®n Akar Aghuim gumazamizibar sure damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Aposel 8:5\x*Ez…® gumazamiziba akar kam baregha bar a gifonge. Egha me Stiven am…®sefe, a gumazir bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itim, ez…® God…®n Duam bar a giz…®fa. Egha me uaghan Filip, ko Prokorus, ko Nikanor, ko Timon, Parmenas, ko Nikolas me am…®sefe. Nikolas an Antiogh…®n gumazim, a Judan gumazim puvat…®, a faragha Judan Arazibagh amuava dar g…®n zui. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n Krais…®n g…®n zui.
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Aposel 13:3; 14:23\x*Ez…® me gumazir kaba inigha aposelbar damazim…®n ghuz…®, me dafariba men dapanibagh is…®n ar…®gha me bagha God ko m…®gei.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt Jon 12:42; Aposel 2:41; 12:24; 16:5; Kolosi 1:6\x*Ez…® God…®n akam bar mogh…®ra ekevegha bar nguibabar ghue. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir suren gumazamizibar d…®bobonim zuam…®ram ekefe. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir av…®rim God…®n akam baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia uaghan an g…®n zui.
\s1 Judan gumaziba Stiven…®n suira
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Aposel 2:43\x*Ez…® God guizbang…®ra Stiven…®n akuragha, apangkuvim ko gavgavim a gan…®ngiz…®ma, a d…®gavir kuram gamir araziba ko mirakel…®n araziba gumazamizibar tong…®n dagh amima da otifi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt 2 Timoti 1:15\x*Ez…® marazi d…®kavigha Stiven ko me m…®g…®r…®g…®abar uari adosi. Me Judan God ko m…®geir d…®penir mam…®n gumaziba, d…®penir kam…®n ziam, Friman. Me Sairinin nguibam…®n gumaziba, ko Aleksandrian nguibam…®n gumaziba, ko Silisian Provins ko Esian Provins…®n gumaziba. Me Stiven ko uari adosi.\f + \fr 6:9 \ft Friman…®n gumazir kaba, me fom…®ra pura ingangarim gamir gumazir k…®niba. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me gumazitam…®n apengan ikia ingarir puvat…®.\f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Aisaia 54:17; Luk 21:15; Aposel 5:39\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam fofozir aghuim isa Stiven gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Judan gumaziba an akaba ko m…®k…®man ibura.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Matyu 26:59-61\x*Ez…® me moga, gumazir mabagh ifara me ab…®ra ghaze, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄúE orazima Stiven m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar Moses ko God gami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® me arazir kam…®n gumazamiziba, ko men gumazir aruaba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazibar navibagh inivima da d…®kafi. Ez…® me Stiven bagha ghugha an suiragha a inigha Judan kot…®n aven itir gumazibar damazim…®n ghue.
