\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt Matyu 10:1; Mak 16:17\x*Me Filip…®n garima a duar kurar gumazamizibagh apazaziba batozima, da pamtem diava arava me atagh…®ragha azenan izi. Ez…® gumazamizir agharir am…®riziba ko suer kurar av…®riba, uaghan ua dera.
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nguibar kam…®n gumazamiziba bar akonge.
\s1 Kukunir gumazim Saimon…®n eghaghanim
\p 
\v 9 Gumazir mam an ziam Saimon, a fom…®ra Samarian nguibam…®n ikia mirakel…®n ifavarir kurabagh amima, Samarian gumazamiziba an ganigha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® gumazir ekiam.‚Äù
