\v 10 Ez…® gumazir ekiaba ko gumazamizir k…®niba, me Saimon…®n akam baraghasa ifonge. Egha me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar aser gavgavim, an ziam Gavgavir Bar Ekiam, a Saimon…®n iti.‚Äù
\v 11 A dughiar av…®ribar mirakel…®n ifavarir kurabagh ami da otivi me dar garava, n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Bizir kam bagha, me an akam baraghasa ifongegha an g…®n arui.
\v 12 Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n Filip, a God Bizibagh Ativir Arazim…®n Akar Aghuim ko Krais Iesus…®n ziam sara kuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Filip…®n akam…®n ikiava, me rue.
\v 13 Ez…® Saimon uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia egha rue. Egha Saimon Filip…®n g…®n arua garima, Filip arazarazir ekiaba ko mirakelbagh amima da otifi, ez…® a d…®gavir kuram gami.
