\v 14 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir aposelba orazima, Samarian gumazamiziba God…®n akam inigha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Pita ko Jon amadaz…® aning me bagha ghu.
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 8:15-16 \xt Matyu 28:19; Aposel 2:38; 10:48; 19:2\x*Samarian gumazamiziba, me Ekiam Iesus…®n ziam…®n ruegha God…®n Duam inizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pita ko Jon ghua otogha, me God…®n Duam iniasa me bagha God ko m…®gei.
\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt Aposel 6:6; 19:6; Hibru 6:2\x*Aning God ko m…®kemegha, uan dafariba me gis…®n ar…®zima me God…®n Duam isi.
