\v 1-2 \x - \xo 9:1-2 \xt Aposel 8:3; Galesia 1:13; 1 Timoti 1:13\x*Dughiar kam…®n Sol Iesus…®n suren gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®gh, me m…®soght…® me ar…®ghirasa, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim gamuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim bagha ghua kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® Damaskus…®n itir God ko m…®geir d…®penibar garir gumazir dapaniba bagh ak…®nafariba osir suam, ‚ÄòGumazitam o amizitam, Iesus…®n Tuavim…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, Sol an apigh, an suiragh mang…®va kalabuziar gumazim…®n m…®n a ik…®rarigh…®va, a inigh Jerusalem…®n mangam.‚Äô ‚Äù
