\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Aposel 22:9; 26:13\x*Ez…® gumazir Sol ko zuiba, me pura gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…®nim baragha gumazitam…®n garir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me m…®g…®r…®g…®aba puvat…®gha pura iti.
