\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Aposel 8:3\x*Ez…® Ananaias a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam, k…® orazima, gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n gumazir kam…®n gun m…®gei, me ghaze, a n…®n gumazir Jerusalem…®n aven itiba paza me gami.
\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt Aposel 9:1-2; 9:21; 22:16; 1 Korin 1:2; 2 Timoti 2:22\x*Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba akar gavgavim an amamangat…®z…® a ize. Egh te n…®n ziam fa n…® ko m…®gei, a men suigh…®va me kalabus dar…®gham.‚Äù
