\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Aposel 17:3; 18:5; 18:28\x*Ez…® Sol akurir akar kabar gavgavim bar ghuanaboz…®, a m…®g…®r…®g…®am bar derav…®rama aneb…®ghiz…®, Judan gumazamizir Damaskus…®n itiba fo, Iesus a Krais, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.
