\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt Aposel 23:12; 25:3; 2 Korin 11:23\x*\x - \xo 9:23-25 \xt 2 Korin 11:32-33\x*Dughiar av…®riba ghua g…®vaz…®ma, Judaba Sol m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buri.
\v 24 Me a m…®soghasava amua, a bagha arueba ko d…®magaribar zurazurara nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akabar gari, ez…® Sol men n…®ghn…®zir kurar kam g…®fo.
