\v 21 \x - \xo 11:21 \xt Aposel 2:41\x*Ez…® Ekiam…®n gavgavim me ko iti. Ez…® gumazamizir bar av…®rim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n ikia egha uan navibagh iragha Ekiam bagha ize.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 11:22 \xt Aposel 4:36\x*Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir Krais…®n adarazi bizir kam…®n eghaghanim baregha, Barnabas amadaz…®ma an Antiogh…®n ghu.
\v 23 \x - \xo 11:23 \xt Aposel 13:43\x*Egha an otogha gari, God men apangkuvigha, men akurvagha arazir aghuibar me gamiz…® Barnabas bar akonge. Egha me uan navir averiabar aven guizbang…®ra Ekiam ko ikiamin m…®g…®r…®g…®abar me m…®gei.
\v 24 \x - \xo 11:24 \xt Aposel 2:41; 5:14; 11:21\x*A bar gumazir aghuim, God…®n Duam a giz…®vaz…® God…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. Ez…® gumazamizir bar av…®rim Ekiam bagha ize.
\p 
\v 25-26 \x - \xo 11:25-26 \xt Aposel 9:30\x*Ez…® Barnabas Sol buriasa Tarsus…®n zui. Egha an apigha, a inigha Antiogh…®n ize. Egha azenir vam…®ra Barnabas ko Sol uaning inigha Krais…®n adarazi ko uari akufa. Egha gumazamizir bar av…®ribar sure gami. Ez…® suren gumaziba Antiok…®n, faragha ziar kam, Krais…®n g…®n zuir darasi, me a ini.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 11:27 \xt Aposel 13:1; 15:32; 21:9; 1 Korin 12:28; Efesus 4:11\x*Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir maba Jerusalem…®n ikegha Antiogh…®n izaghiri.
\v 28 \x - \xo 11:28 \xt Aposel 21:10\x*Ez…® men mav, an ziam Agabus, a d…®kavigha God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, Rom…®n nguaziba bar dagheba otevegham. (Sisar Klodius, atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n bizir kam oto.)
\v 29 \x - \xo 11:29 \xt Rom 15:26; 1 Korin 16:1; 2 Korin 9:1\x*Ez…® suren gumaziba akam m…®suegha, vaghvagh uan dabirabim…®n m…®n dag…®aba dan…®ng…®va, Judian itir darazir akurvaghasa dag…®aba amangasa.
\v 30 \x - \xo 11:30 \xt Aposel 12:25\x*Me kamagh…®n amigha, uan dag…®aba isa, Barnabas ko Sol gan…®ngiz…®, aning ghua Krais…®n adarazir gumazir dapanibagh an…®ngi.
\c 12
\s1 Herot Jems m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, a Pita kalabus gat…®
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Atrivim Herot Krais…®n adarazir marazir suigha me gas…®ghas…®ghasa.\f + \fr 12:1 \ft Atrivir kam Herot, a Maria Iesus batezir dughiam…®n itir Atrivir kam Herot…®n ovavir borim. Egha a Atrivim Agripan afeziam.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Matyu 4:21; 20:23\x*Egha a m…®geima, me Jon…®n aveghbuam Jems m…®dorozir sabam…®n a m…®soghez…®, an areme.
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Aposel 4:3\x*Ez…® Herot garima, an amizir arazir kam, Judaba a gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uaghan Pitan suiragha a isa kalabus gat…®. Herot Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam…®n Dughiam…®n bizir kam gami.
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:1-27\x*A Pitan suiragha a isa kalabus gat…®. Egha a isa m…®dorozir gumazir 4plan okoruabar agharim gat…®. Ez…® me dughiaba isa vaghvagha an gari. Egha 4plan okoruar kaba, me dar vaghvagha 4plan gumaziba iniz…®ma me an gari. Herot, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n Isar Ekiar kam g…®vaght…®, a Pita is…® gumazamizir av…®ribar damazim…®n a kot dar…®ghasa.
\v 5 \x - \xo 12:5 \xt Jems 5:16\x*Ez…® Pita kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n aven itima Krais…®n adarazi uan navir averiabar a bagha puv…®ra God ko m…®g…®av…®ra iti.
\s1 Ensel kalabuziar d…®penim…®n Pita inigha azenim gat…®
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt Aposel 5:23\x*Egha Herot Pita inigh kot bagh mangasa dughiar mam d…®boro. Ez…® d…®magarir kam…®n, am…®nim t…®ghar tiam, me sen…®n pumuning…®n a ikez…® a m…®dorozir gumazir pumuning…®n tong…®n akui. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir igharazir maba kalabuziar d…®penim…®n a bagha gara tiar akam…®n iti.
\v 7 Ez…® zuam…®ra Ekiam…®n ensel otoz…®, an angazangarim kalabuziar d…®penim…®n aven sira. Egha ensel Pitan ivim am…®suegha a gaghuragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® zuam…®ra d…®kafigh!‚Äù Ez…® sen…®n an agharimning gikezimning f…®riagh…®r…®gha nguazim gir…®.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® ensel a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® korotiam arugh…®va dagarir asuabar aghuigh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Pita kamagh…®n amigha g…®vaz…® ensel a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan korotiar ruarim arugh nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt Aposel 10:3; 10:17; 11:5\x*Ez…® Pita kalabuziar d…®penim ategha, ensel…®n g…®n azenan ghu. A bizir kabagh fozir puvat…®z…®, ensel dagh amima, da guizbang…®ram otifi. Pitan n…®ghn…®zim ghaze, a irebam…®n m…®n bizim…®n gari.
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Onger Akaba 34:7; Daniel 6:22; Aposel 5:19; Hibru 1:14; 2 Pita 2:9\x*Aning ghuava, kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazir pumuning gitagha, ghua kalabus…®n zuir ain…®n tiar akar nguibar ekiam…®n zuim…®n oto. Aning an otoz…®, tiam uab…® kuiaghir…®z…®ma, aning azenan ghua tuavir mam…®n zui. Aning mong saghon ghua, ensel zuam…®ra Pita ategha ghu.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Pitan n…®ghn…®zim ua izima, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®ra fo, Ekiam uan ensel amadaz…®ma a ize. Egha a Herot…®n agharim da nan akura, egha Judaba na damuasa n…®ghn…®zir bizir kuraba sara nan akura.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 12:12 \xt Aposel 4:23; 12:5; 15:37\x*Pita bizir kabagh fogha, Jon…®n amebam Marian d…®penim…®n ghu. Jon…®n ziar mam Mak. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rim uari akuvagha d…®penir kam…®n ikia God ko m…®gei.
\v 13 Ez…® Pita azenan ikia d…®vazim…®n tiar akar azenan itim gafughafuzima, ingangarir amizim…®n ziam Roda, a bagha tiam kuasa izi.
\v 14 Egha a Pitan tiarim baregha, bar akuegha, tiam kuizir puvat…®gha uamategha ivegha aven ghua, kamagh…®n gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúPita muna iza tiar akam…®n iti!‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 12:15 \xt Matyu 18:10; Aposel 26:24\x*Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® onganis ti.‚Äù
\p Ez…® a bar gavgavigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Guizbang…®ra a iti.‚Äù
\p Ez…® me a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ti an ensel…®n gani.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:15 \ft Dughiar kam Judan av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, ensel…®n maba gumazamizibar ganamin ingangariba iti. Egha me ghaze, Pitan ensel markiama.\f*
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Pita tiam gafughafuzima, me iza tiam kuigha an apigha, d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 17 Ez…® Pita uan dafarim…®n me aminivaz…®ma, me aghumra iti. Ez…® an Ekiam kalabuziar d…®penim…®n aven a inigha azenan anet…®zir arazibagh eghari. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bizir kabar gun Jems ko aveghbuaba sara m…®kemegh.‚Äù Egha Pita me ategha danganir igharazim…®n ghu.\f + \fr 12:17 \ft Jems…®n kam a Iesus…®n dozim. N…® Galesian 1:19…®n gan. Jems Jerusalem…®n sios…®n itir gumazir dapanim…®n oto.\f*
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 12:18 \xt Aposel 5:22-24\x*Egha am…®nim tiraz…®ma, m…®dorozir gumaziba Pita bagh garava avenge. Egha bar d…®gavir kuram gamigha uarira uarir azangs…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúPita managh ghu?‚Äù
\v 19 Pita itir puvat…®z…®, Herot a gumazibav kemez…® me Pita buriasa ghue. Egha me tong bar an apizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…® m…®dorozir gumazir a Pitan ganasa ar…®ghiziba, Herot me isa kot gat…®gha ghaze, me ar…®m…®ghiram. Egha Herot g…®n Judian danganim ategha, Sisarian nguibar ekiam…®n ikiasa uaghir…®.
\s1 Herot…®n ovevem
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt 1 Atriviba 5:9-11; Esekiel 27:17\x*Egha Herot adarim Tair ko Saidonian gumazamizibar iti. Me Herot garir nguibar ekiam…®n uan dagheba isi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me dat…®r…®gh…®n uari akuvagha izi an ganasa. Me faragha Blastus ko uariv kemez…® a me ko navir am…®rizim inis. Blastus, an Atrivim Herot akuir danganim…®n garir gumazim. Egha g…®n, me Herot…®n ganasa zui, Herot men apangkuvigh adarir kam me kom aneg…®vagham.
\p 
\v 21 Herot dughiar at…®zim…®n, a uan atrivir korotiaba aghuigha, uan atrivim…®n dabirabim gaperagha gumazamizibav gei.
\v 22 Ez…® me pamtem d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar gumazim m…®geir puvat…®. Kar god…®n mam m…®gei.‚Äù
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt 1 Samuel 25:38; 2 Samuel 24:17; Onger Akaba 115:1; Daniel 5:20\x*Herot God…®n ziam fer puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ekiam…®n ensel magh…®ra a m…®soghez…® a ir…®. Ez…® apiziba angam…®ra anepa zuima, an areme.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 12:24 \xt Aisaia 55:11; Aposel 6:7; 19:20; Kolosi 1:6\x*Ez…® God…®n akam nguibaba bar dar ghua bar ekevegha ghuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 12:25 \xt Aposel 11:29-30; 13:5; 13:13; 15:37\x*Ez…® Barnabas ko Sol uan ingangarim Jerusalem…®n aneg…®vagha, uamategha Antiogh…®n ghu. Jon, an ziar mam Mak, aning a inigha a sara ghu.
\c 13
\ms1 Pol kantrin av…®ribar ghua Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim akuri
\mr (Sapta 13:1--21:14)
\s1 God kantrin igharazibar Akar Aghuim akunasa Barnabas ko Sol am…®sefe
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Aposel 11:27\x*Antiogh…®n itir Krais…®n adarasi, men marazi God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba ko tisaba. Men ziabar kara: Barnabas, ko Simeon (an ziar mam Niger) ko Sairinin gumazim Lusius, ko Manain (a Atrivim Herot…®n roroam, a Herot koma aghungi) ko Sol.\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Ziar kam Niger, an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚Äúp…®zim.‚Äù Gumazir maba ghaze, Simeon Niger, a Afrikan gumazim.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Aposel 9:15; Rom 10:15; Galesia 1:15; Efesus 3:7-8; 1 Timoti 2:7; Hibru 5:4\x*Ez…® dughiar mam…®n Krais…®n adarasi, me God…®n apengan ikia uari isa God gan…®ga, God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba ta. Ez…® God…®n Duam kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Barnabas ko Sol uan ingangarim bagha aning…®n dia. Ia ingangarir kam bagh aning am…®seveght…®, aning nan ingangarim bagh mang…®.‚Äù
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt Aposel 6:6\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba tagha, God ko m…®gei. Egha uan dafariba Barnabas ko Sol gis…®n at…®gha, aning amadaz…® aning zui.
\s1 Barnabas ko Sol Saiprus…®n Arighat…®zim…®n Akar Aghuim akuri
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt Aposel 15:39\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam Barnabas ko Sol amadaz…®, aning Selusian nguibar ekiam…®n ghugha, ua kurim inigha Saiprus…®n Arighat…®zim…®n ghu.
\v 5 \x - \xo 13:5 \xt Aposel 12:12; 12:25; 13:13; 13:46; 15:37\x*Egha me Salamis…®n otivigha Judaba God ko m…®geir d…®penibar, God…®n akam akuri. Jon Mak aning ko ghua aning…®n akura.
\p 
\v 6 Me Saiprus…®n nguibar arighat…®zim bar a garua ghua, Pafos…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Egha me Judan kukunir gumazir mam bato. A God…®n akam inigha izir ifavarir gumazim, an ziam Bar-Iesus.
\v 7 A gavman…®n gumazir dapanim Sergius Paulus ko iti. Sergius Paulus, a gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozir aghuiba itim. A God…®n akam baraghasa, egha kamagh…®n a Pol ko Barnabas…®n diaz…® aning ize.
\v 8 \x - \xo 13:8 \xt 2 Timoti 3:8\x*Kukunir gumazir kam, me Grigh…®n akam…®n ziar kam Elimas a gat…®, an m…®ngarim kukunir gumazim. Elimas, a gavman…®n gumazim Sergius Paulus, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikian an aghua. Elimas, Barnabas ko Sol…®n ingangarim paz…®va a damuasa.
\v 9 Ez…® Sol, an ziar mam Pol, God…®n Duam a giz…®vaz…®ma, a d…®k…®rav…®ra Elimas…®n gara kamagh…®n m…®gei,\f + \fr 13:9 \ft Ziar kam Sol, a Hibrun akam…®n otivir ziar mam. Ez…® ziar kam Pol, a Grigh…®n akam otivir ziam. Gumazir maba ghaze, Sol Grigh…®n akam…®n m…®geir darazir tong…®n ingara, egha kamagh…®n dughiar kam…®n a ziar kam Pol uab…® gar…®si.\f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Matyu 13:38; Jon 8:44; 1 Jon 3:8\x*‚ÄúN…® Satan…®n borim. N…® arazir aghuaribar apanim…®n iti. Ifavarir araziba ko arazir kuraba bar n…® giz…®fa. Egha n…® tizim baghav…®ra Ekiam…®n arazir aghuibagh as…®ghas…®si? N…® ti arazir kuraba atagh…®raghan aghua?
\v 11 \x - \xo 13:11 \xt Ua Me Ini 9:3; 1 Samuel 5:6; Aposel 9:8\x*Dat…®r…®gh…®n Ekiam n…®n apanim damu uan gavgavim…®n n…®n damazimning okavigham. Eght…® n…® aruer angazangarim…®n ganan kogh dughiatabar ikegham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® zuam…®ra ghuariam an damazimning koroz…® am…®nim an p…®ri. Ez…® a tav…®n agharim…®n suighasa pura ruia asaghinifi.
\v 12 Ez…® gavman…®n gumazir dapanim, Ekiam…®n akam baregha d…®gavir kuram gami. A bizir otivizir kabar ganigha, kamagh…®n a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n iti.
\s1 Barnabas ko Pol Antiogh…®n aven Iesus…®n akam akuri
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 13:13 \xt Aposel 13:5; 15:38\x*Ez…® Pol ko gumazir a koma aruiba, me Pafos…®n kurim inigha ghua Pergan nguibam…®n otifi. A Pamfilian Provins…®n aven iti. Ez…® Jon Mak kagh me ategha uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu.
\v 14 Ez…® me Pergan nguibam…®n d…®kavigha ghua Antiogh…®n nguibam…®n otifi, a Pisidian Distrigh…®n aven iti. Egha, Judaba avughsa God…®n ziam fer dughiam…®n, me God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghuegha apiaghav iti.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft A Sabat…®n dughiam.\f*
\v 15 \x - \xo 13:15 \xt Luk 4:16; Aposel 13:27; 15:21; Hibru 13:22\x*Ez…® God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n garir gumazir dapanir ekiaba, me Moses Osirizir Araziba ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba dar bora me m…®gei. Me dar ponegha g…®vagha, Pol ko Barnabas bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúAveghbuaba, ia akurvazir m…®g…®r…®g…®atam gumazir kabav k…®ms…®, ia me m…®k…®m.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Pol d…®kavigha, uan dafarim…®n me aminiva, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Israel…®n gumazamiziba ko, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir God…®n atiatia uari isa God gan…®diba, ia na baragh!
\v 17 \x - \xo 13:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 1:7; 6:6; God…®n Araziba 7:6-7; Onger Akaba 105:23-24\x*Fom…®ra Israel…®n gumazamizibar God en ovaviba am…®sevez…®ma, kamagh…®n me an gumazamizibara. Egha g…®n me uan nguibam ategha ghua Isip…®n kantrin ghue. Egha dughiar kam…®n God me gamima men d…®bobonim bar p…®n ghua, me bar av…®raseme. Ez…®ma g…®n God uan gavgavim…®n Isip…®n me inighava azenim gat…®.
\v 18 \x - \xo 13:18 \xt Ua Me Ini 16:35; D…®boboniba 14:34; God…®n Araziba 1:31; Onger Akaba 95:10; Aposel 7:36\x*Egha a 40plan azenibar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim me ko ikia, men os…®mt…®ziba atera men akurvasi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 13:19 \xt God…®n Araziba 7:1; Josua 14:1; Onger Akaba 78:55\x*Egha Kenan…®n nguaziba, God 7plan gumazamizir b…®zim gas…®ghas…®gha, men nguaziba isa uan gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® me dar ghuaviba ikiangi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 13:20 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 2:16; 1 Samuel 3:20\x*Bizir kaba 450 azenim…®n aven otifi.
\p ‚ÄúEgha bizir kabar g…®n God Israelian ganasa gumazir dapaniba am…®s…®va, mamagh…®ra ikia ghua, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Samuel…®n dughiam…®n tu.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Samuel 8:5; 8:19; 10:1; 10:21\x*‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n Israelia atrivim bagha God…®n azangs…®si. Ez…® a Sol me gan…®ngi, a Kis…®n otarim, egha Benjamin…®n adarazir gumazim, a 40plan azenibar men gari.
\v 22 \x - \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Samuel 13:14; 15:23-26; 16:12-13; 2 Samuel 2:4; Onger Akaba 89:20; Hosea 13:11\x*Ez…® God Sol ag…®vagha, Devit am…®sevez…® an an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® a Devit…®n gun me m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® Devit…®n gani, Jesin otarim, gumazir k…® bar ifongezim, bizir k…® ifongeziba a bar dar amuam.‚Äô
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 13:23 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12-16; Onger Akaba 132:11; Aisaia 11:1; Luk 1:32; 1:69; Rom 11:26\x*‚ÄúGod fom…®ra akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, God gumazir mam amadaz…® a Israel…®n ize. A Iesus, Devit…®n ovavir mam, a en Akurvazir Gumazim.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 13:24 \xt Matyu 3:1-2; Mak 1:4; Luk 3:3; Rom 11:26\x*‚ÄúIesus t…®ghar izamin dughiam…®n, Jon faragha izava navibagh iraghamin akam ko rurum…®n akam…®n Israel…®n gumazamizibav gei.
\v 25 \x - \xo 13:25 \xt Matyu 3:11; Mak 1:7; Luk 3:16; Jon 1:20-27\x*Jon…®n ingangarir dughiam g…®vasava amima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa ghaze, k…® tina? K…® gumazir ia m…®zua itim puvat…®. A nan g…®n izi. K…® an dagarir asuabar beniba f…®ran derazir puvat…®. K…® gumazir k…®nim.‚Äô
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 13:26 \xt Matyu 10:6; Luk 24:47; Aposel 13:46\x*‚ÄúAveghbuaba, ia Abraham…®n igiaba, ko ia God gifuegha an apengan itir Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, e bagha, God uam e iniasa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam amadaz…® a ize.
\v 27 \x - \xo 13:27 \xt Luk 23:34; 24:20; 24:44; Jon 16:3; Aposel 3:17; 15:21; 1 Korin 2:8\x*Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba ko gumazir ekiaba, me kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Iesus en Akurvazir Gumazim. Egha me zurara Sabat…®n dughiam…®n God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akaba d…®bora, egha deragha dagh fozir puvat…®. Egha ghaze gumazir kam aremegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n akaba guizbang…®ra otos.
\v 28 \x - \xo 13:28 \xt Matyu 27:22-23; Mak 15:13-14; Luk 23:21-23; Jon 19:15\x*Egha me a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir aghuitam batozir puvat…®. Ez…® me pamtem kamagh…®n Pailat m…®gei, n…® m…®dorozir gumazibav kemeght…® me a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 29 \x - \xo 13:29 \xt Matyu 27:57-61; Mak 15:42-47; Luk 18:31; 23:50-56; Jon 19:28-30; 19:36-42\x*God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba fom…®ra m…®kemez…® mogh…®n me ami. Egha me ter ighuvim…®n anedegha a inigha dag…®ar torim gat…®.
\v 30 \x - \xo 13:30 \xt Matyu 28:6; Aposel 2:24\x*Ez…® God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 13:31 \xt Aposel 1:3; 1:8\x*A ko Galilin Distrigh…®n ikia Jerusalem…®n zuir gumazamiziba, me dughiar av…®ribar an gani. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir uari an ganizir kaba, me an gun Judan gumazamizibav gei.
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 13:32 \xt Aposel 13:23; Rom 4:13; Galesia 3:16\x*‚ÄúE Akar Aghuim kamagh…®n ia m…®gei. God fom…®ra en ovaviba bagha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a gumazir uam e iniamim amadagham.
\v 33 \x - \xo 13:33 \xt Onger Akaba 2:7; Rom 1:4; Hibru 1:5; 5:5\x*Dat…®r…®gh…®n, a Iesus gamiz…® a matmat…®n ua d…®kafi. E men boriba, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an e bagha uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam gamiz…® a guizbang…®ram oto. Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim sapta 2, kamagh…®n a m…®gei:
