\v 45 \x - \xo 13:45 \xt Aposel 14:2; 18:6; 1 Pita 4:4; Jut 1:10\x*Ez…® Judaba gumazamizir okoruar kam…®n ganigha, men naviba bar ikufi. Ez…® me Pol…®n akabar kurakuragha a m…®gei.
