\v 46 \x - \xo 13:46 \xt Aisaia 55:5; Luk 7:30; Aposel 3:26; 18:6; Rom 1:16; 10:19\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pol ko Barnabas atiatir puvat…®gha, akar bar gavgavim…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judaba, ga faragha God…®n akam…®n ia m…®keme. Ez…® ia ak…®rim ragha akar kam gasara. Egha ghaze, e ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir zurara itim inian kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia oragh, ga uam akar kam…®n ia m…®k…®man kogham. Ga Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibav k…®mam.
\v 47 \x - \xo 13:47 \xt Aisaia 42:6; 49:6; Luk 2:32\x*Ekiam bizir kam bagha kamagh…®n e m…®keme:
