\v 14 Ez…® aposelning Pol ko Barnabas, aning bizir kaba baregha, uan korotiaba ab…®agharigha, ivegha gumazamizibar okoruam…®n aven ghua pamtem d…®a m…®gei,
\v 15 \x - \xo 14:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:11; Onger Akaba 33:6; 146:6; Aposel 10:26; 1 Korin 8:4; 1 Tesalonika 1:9; Jems 5:17\x*‚ÄúMaia! Gumazamiziba, ia tizim bagha arazir kam gami? Ga pura gumazir k…®nimning, egha uaghan ian m…®rara gari. Ga kamaghsua Akar Aghuir kam ia m…®gei. Ia pura bizir k…®nir kabar ziaba fan mark…®. Ia uari is…® Ekiam dan…®ng, an Angam…®ra Itir God. A God…®n overiam ko nguazim ko ongarim…®n ingarizim, egha dar itir biziba bar adar ingari.
\v 16 \x - \xo 14:16 \xt Onger Akaba 81:12; Aposel 17:30; 1 Pita 4:3\x*Fom…®ra, God nguibaba bar, me ataghiz…®ma me pura uan n…®ghn…®zibar arua bizibagh ami.
\v 17 \x - \xo 14:17 \xt Onger Akaba 147:8; Jeremaia 5:24; 14:22; Aposel 17:27; Rom 1:20\x*Egha a ian modozir puvat…®, eght…® gumazamiziba a g…®foghan kogham. Puvat…®. A zuraram arazir aghuibar ia gamua, amozim ia gan…®ga, dagher aghuir av…®riba ia gan…®ga, dagher aghuibagh ami da otifi. Egha ia gamima ian naviba deragha bar akonge.‚Äù
