\v 19 \x - \xo 14:19 \xt Aposel 13:45; 17:13; 2 Korin 11:25; 2 Timoti 3:11\x*Ez…® g…®n Judan gumazir maba Antiok ko Aikoniam…®n ikegha Listran izegha, gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh ekuiz…®, me Pol…®n apanibar otifi. Egha me dag…®abar Pol ginivigha an ganigha ghaze, an areme. Egha anem…®k…®r…®gha Listran nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ghu.
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n suren gumazamiziba iza an okariz…®, a d…®kavigha uamategha Listran nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Egha dughiar igharazim…®n a Barnabas ko Derben zui.
\s1 Pol ko Barnabas gavgavim isa suren gumazamizibagh an…®di
