\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Matyu 28:19\x*Pol ko Barnabas Derben nguibar ekiam…®n ikia Akar Aghuim akura gumazamizir av…®ribagh ami, me suren gumazamizibar otifi. Egha aning uamategha Listra ko Aikoniam ko Antiogh…®n ghu.
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt Matyu 7:14; Aposel 11:23; 15:32; 18:23; 1 Tesalonika 3:3\x*Aning gavgavim suren gumazamizibagh an…®ga akurvazir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar me gamua ghaze, ia uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar tuivigh gavgafigh. Aning kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE God Bizibagh Ativaghamin Dughiam…®n aven mang…®s…®, e faragh os…®mt…®zir av…®ribar aven mang…®gham.‚Äù
\v 23 \x - \xo 14:23 \xt Aposel 15:40\x*Egha Pol ko Barnabas Krais…®n adarazi itir nguibaba bagha vaghvagha gumazamizir dapaniba am…®sefe. Gumazamizir dapanir kaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba Ekiam…®n iti. Ez…® aning me bagha dagheba tagha Ekiam ko m…®kemegha me isava Ekiam…®n agharim gat…®.
