\v 26 \x - \xo 14:26 \xt Aposel 13:1-3; 15:40\x*Egha aning Atalian ikegha kurim inigha uamategha Antiogh…®n nguibam…®n ghu. Nguibar kamra, aning kagh faragha ikez…®, Antiogh…®n itir Krais…®n adarazi aning isa God…®n agharim gan…®ga ghaze, God…®n apangkuvim aning ko ik…®t…® aning ingangarir kam damuam. Ez…® aning ingangarir kam gamua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n aneg…®vagha, uamategha Antiogh…®n ghu.
\v 27 \x - \xo 14:27 \xt Aposel 11:18; 15:4; 15:12\x*Egha aning Antiogh…®n otogha, Krais…®n adarazir diaz…® me iza uari akuvaz…®ma, aning bizir God aning…®n dafaribar amiziba bar, dar gun me m…®gei. Egha uaghan God Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bagha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tiam kuizir akam me m…®gei.
\v 28 Egha aning kagh dughiar ruarim…®n suren gumazamiziba ko ike.
\c 15
\s1 Krais…®n adarazi Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n uari akufa
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt Ofa Gami 12:3; Jon 7:22; Galesia 2:12; 5:2; Kolosi 2:11; 2:16\x*Ez…® Judian Distrigh…®n gumazir maba Antiogh…®n izegha Krais…®n adarazir sure gamua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Moses…®n Arazim…®n g…®n mangan kogh, egh uan m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoreghan koght…®, God ua ia inighan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Gumazir kaba me Judan gumaziba, egha me ghaze, gumazir azenan itiba me en arazibar amuam. Men marazi fom…®ra Farisibar ike.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Aposel 11:30; Galesia 2:1\x*Bizir kam bang…®n, Pol ko Barnabas maburan odorozim me koma a gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Krais…®n adarazi Pol ko Barnabas ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir gumazir maba sara me am…®sevegha ghaze, me Jerusalem…®n mang…® bizir kam bagh aposelba ko Sios…®n gumazamizir dapanibav k…®mam.
