\v 3 Egha Krais…®n adarazi, me amadaz…®ma me zui. Me Fonisian Distrik ko Samarian mogh…®n ghua Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uan navibagh irazir bizim…®n gun me m…®gei. Ez…® Krais…®n adarazi bar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha bar akonge.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 15:4 \xt Aposel 14:27\x*Ez…® Pol ko Barnabas, me ko zui darazi ko, me Jerusalem…®n otiviz…®, aposelba ko Krais…®n adarazi ko men gumazir dapaniba bar akuegha me ini. Ez…® Pol ko Barnabas God aning…®n agharim…®n amizir bizibar, gun me m…®gei.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir gumazir maba, me fom…®ra Farisibar m…®n ike, me d…®kavigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uaghan Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®va uan m…®karzir mogomebar aghor.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:5 \ft N…® akar Filipai, 3:2…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
