\v 37 Ez…® Pol kamagh…®n polis…®n gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúGa Rom…®n gumazimning. Me ga isa kot gat…®zir puvat…®gha gumazir av…®ribar damazim…®n pura ga m…®sogha, ga isa kalabus…®n ga amada. Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®m…®ra ga amangasa? Ti puvat…®gham! Me uari iz…®va gan aku mangam.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:37 \ft Dughiar kam…®n Rom…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim, an ziam Sisar. A Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n borogh…®ra itir kantribar gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Rom…®n kantrin itir gumaziba mati gumazir ziar ekiaba iti mogh…®n iti. Ez…® men osirizir arazim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Kotiaba ko gavman…®n gumaziba pura me m…®soghan kogham. Dughiar mabar Romba, gumazir igharaziba uaghan me ataghiz…®ma me uaghan Rom…®n kantrin gumazibar m…®n otifi. Pol…®n afeziam a uaghan kamagh…®n amizir gumazir mam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pol…®n amebam a batez…®, a uaghan Rom…®n kantrin gumazir mam. (N…® Aposel 22:24-29 an ganigh.)\f*
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® polis…®n gumaziba akar kabar gun jasbav keme. Ez…® me orazi Pol ko Sailas Rom…®n gumazimning. Ez…® me atiatingi.
\v 39 \x - \xo 16:39 \xt Matyu 8:34\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, jasba kalabus…®n d…®penim…®n ghuegha, kamagh…®n aning m…®g…®a ghaze, gua ataran mark…®. Egha me aning…®n akua azenan ghuegha, aning…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄúGua nguibar ekiar kam ategh mang…®.‚Äù
\v 40 Ez…® aning kalabus…®n d…®penim ategha Lidian d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha Krais…®n adarazir ganigha, akar maba me m…®g…®a, gavgavim me ganigha, egha aning ghu.
\c 17
\s1 Me Tesalonikan nguibam…®n aven akam akuri
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt 1 Tesalonika 1:1-2; 2:1-2\x*Pol ko an g…®n aruir gumaziba, me Amfipolis ko Apolonian nguibamning ategha ghuav…®ra ikia Tesalonikan nguibam…®n oto. Tesalonikan nguibam…®n aven, Judabar d…®penir God ko m…®geir mam iti.
\v 2 Egha Pol God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghu. Kar a zuraram amir arazim. Egha Sabat…®n pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir osiziriba me geghara me m…®gei.
\v 3 \x - \xo 17:3 \xt Luk 24:26; Aposel 3:18; 9:22; 18:28; Galesia 3:1\x*An osiziriba men akakagha dar m…®ngaribav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKrais m…®zazim inigh aremegh ua d…®kavamin m…®g…®r…®g…®am, a guizbang…®ra.‚Äù
\p Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIesus…®n k…® akam akurir kamnagh, a Gumazir God Ua Gumazamiziba Iniasa M…®sevezim, a Krais.‚Äù\f + \fr 17:3 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim, Krais, kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúGod Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim.‚Äù\f*
\v 4 \x - \xo 17:4 \xt Aposel 13:50; 15:22; 15:27; 15:40; 28:24\x*Ez…® Judan gumazir maba oregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim akar kabar ikia Pol ko Sailas…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® uaghan God…®n atiatir Grigh…®n gumazir av…®riba ko ziaba itir amizir av…®riba sara aning…®n g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 5 Gumazir av…®rim Pol ko Sailas…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n zuima, Judaba kamagh…®n naviba bar ikufi. Egha puram aruir gumazir kurar maba akumakumigha gumazir b…®zir dafam gami. Egha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n aven arua pamtem atarava araghasi. Me Pol ko Sailas inigh av…®rir torim…®n mangasa, aning buriasa ivemara Jeson…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghue.
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt Aposel 16:20\x*Egha me aning…®n apizir puvat…®gha, Jeson ko Krais…®n marazi kur…®vegha nguibar ekiam…®n garir gumazir dapaniba bagha me inigha ghu. Egha kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúGumazir kaba os…®mt…®zim nguazir kam…®n nguibaba bar dagh ar…®gha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n kagh oto.
\v 7 \x - \xo 17:7 \xt Luk 23:2; Jon 19:12; 1 Pita 2:13\x*Ez…® Jeson me inigha uan d…®penim gat…®. Gumazir kaba bar mogh…®ra Sisar osirizir arazibar g…®n mangan aghua. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, Atrivir ekiar igharazim uaghan iti, an ziam Iesus.‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®rir uari akuvaziba ko nguibar ekiam…®n garir gumazir dapaniba, me men akar kam baragha d…®gavir kuram gamigha diava arai.
\v 9 Egha nguibar ekiam…®n garir gumazir dapaniba, me Jeson ko an adaraziv kemez…®, me sel givese. Ez…® me me ataghiz…®, me zui.
\s1 Berian nguibam…®n itir Judabar arazir aghuim
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® am…®nim p…®rima, Krais…®n adarazi zuam…®ra aning amadaz…® aning Berian nguibam…®n ghu. Aning ghua otivav…®ra Judabar d…®penir God ko m…®geim…®n aven ghu.
\v 11 \x - \xo 17:11 \xt Aisaia 34:16; Luk 16:29; Jon 5:39\x*Berian Judaba, men araziba ko men n…®ghn…®ziba bar dera. Me Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraghasa bar ifonge. Egha me Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®ngariba ab…®gh bar dagh fofoghasa zurara God…®n Akam…®n Osiziribar gari. Me kamagh…®n foghasa, Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da guiz…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, o? Kamagh…®n, me Tesalonikan itir Judabar arazibagh afira.
\v 12 Ez…® Judan av…®riba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar iti. Ez…® uaghan Grigh…®n amizir ziaba itir maba ko Grigh…®n gumazir av…®riba sara aning…®n g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 17:13 \xt Aposel 13:50; 14:19\x*Ez…® Judan gumazir Tesalonikan itiba orazi, Pol Berian ikia God…®n akam akuri. Ez…® me uaghan Berian otivigha gumazamizir kabar n…®ghn…®zim gas…®ghas…®gha men navibagh inifi.
\v 14 Ez…® Krais…®n adarazi zuam…®ra Pol amadaz…® an ongarir m…®riam…®n ghu. Sailas ko Timoti Berian ikiav…®ra iti.
\v 15 Ez…® Pol…®n akua zuir gumaziba, ghua Atens…®n anet…®. Ez…® Pol, Sailas ko Timoti zuam…®ra a bativasa, an aning bagha akam isa me gan…®ngi.
\s1 Pol Atens…®n ikiava akam akuri
\p 
\v 16 Egha Pol Atens…®n ikia Sailas ko Timoti bagha m…®zuai. Egha a gari, Atens…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven marvir guaba bar iz…®fa. Ez…® Pol bar osemegha an muriam bar ikufi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt Aposel 18:19\x*Egha a bizir kam bagha God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven a Judaba ko Grigh…®n God…®n atiatia itir gumazamiziba sara m…®gei. Egha uaghan bizibagh ivezir danganim…®n zurara gumazir pura iza otivibav gei.
\v 18 Ez…® Epikurian ko Stoik…®n gumazir fofoziba itiba, me Pol ko uari adosi. Marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOnganir mam tizibav gei?‚Äù Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA ti aser igharazibar akam akuri.‚Äù Pol Iesus ua d…®kavizir bizim…®n Akar Aghuim akurima, kamagh…®n me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabar a gami.\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Faragha zuir akam, Grighbar tong…®n gumazir av…®riba, me fofozir gumazir fom…®ra ikezibar n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n zui. Men fofozir gumazibar mamning, aning ziamning Epikurian ko Stoik.\f*
\p 
\v 19-20 Egha me a inigha Atens…®n garir gumazir dapanibar tong…®n ghua me m…®ghs…®am…®n Areopagus uari akuvagha iti. Egha me kamagh…®n Pol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® n…®ghn…®zir e fom…®ra tong oraghizir puvat…®zibav gei. E dar m…®ngarim g…®foghasa ifonge. Kamagh…®n e foghasa, kar n…®ghn…®zir igiar manam, n…® an gumazamizibar sure gami. N…® e m…®k…®m.‚Äù
\v 21 (Atens…®n gumaziba ko Atens…®n azenan itir gumazir izeziba, me zurara pura ikiava n…®ghn…®zir igiar otivir kabara m…®gei.)
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Pol Areopagus…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tong…®ra tugha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Atens…®n gumaziba! K…® ian gari, ia god…®n m…®n asebar g…®n mangasa bar gavgafi.
\v 23 K…® arua bar derav…®ra bizir ia ziaba febar gani, egha k…® uaghan ofa gamir dakozir mam…®n gari ziar kam an iti: E fozir puvat…®zir god…®n ofa gamir dakozim. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…®, god…®n ia fozir puvat…®gha g…®n zuim, k…® an akam ia m…®k…®masa.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 17:24 \xt Matyu 11:25; Aposel 7:48; 14:15\x*\x - \xo 17:24-25 \xt 1 Atriviba 8:27; Aisaia 42:5\x*‚ÄúGod…®n mam iti, a nguazir kam ko an itir biziba bar dar ingari, anar…®ra overiam ko nguazim…®n Ekiam. Egha a gumaziba dafaribar ingarir d…®penibar itir puvat…®.
\v 25 \x - \xo 17:25 \xt Jop 12:10; Onger Akaba 50:12; Sekaraia 12:1; Aposel 7:48\x*God…®n kam a uab…® ik…®r…®m…®rim ko biziba bar gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Egha a bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, e uan dafaribar an akurvagh bizitam damighan kogham.
\v 26 Ez…® God gumazir vam…®ran ingari, egha an ovavir kam…®n a gumazamiziba bar men ingari. Egha me isa nguazim…®n danganiba bar dagh ar…®ki. Egha a uab…® me ikiamin ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n dughiaba ar…®ki. Egha danganir me itiba a me bagha nguazir m…®taghniaba ar…®ki.
\v 27 \x - \xo 17:27 \xt Onger Akaba 145:18; Aisaia 55:6; Jeremaia 23:23; Aposel 14:17; Rom 1:20\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, gumazamiziba a buri, an borogh…®n iz…®va an apigh, kamagh…®n a bizir kabagh ami. Guizbang…®ra God e vaghvagha en saghon itir puvat…®.
\v 28 \x - \xo 17:28 \xt Kolosi 1:17; Hibru 1:3\x*‚ÄòAnar…®ra e gamima, e ikiava, aruava egha ik…®r…®m…®rim isi.‚Äô Ez…® ian fofozir gumazir mabara kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòE God…®n boribara.‚Äô\f + \fr 17:28 \ft Pol gumazir kaba an akam derav…®ra ag…®foghasa, egha a men fom…®ra itir Grigh…®n gumazibar akar otevir pumuning isa, uan akam gavgavim a dan…®ngasa, aning gun me m…®gei.\f*
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 17:29 \xt Aisaia 40:18-20; 44:10-17; Aposel 19:26\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, e guizbang…®ra an ovavibar ik…®va, egh kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogh suam, God ti gol…®n nedazim o silvan nedazim o dag…®abar nedazim. E uaghan kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogh suam, a ti gumazamiziba uari uan dafariba ko uan n…®ghn…®zibar ingarizir marvir guatam.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 17:30 \xt Aposel 14:16; Rom 3:25; Taitus 2:11-12; 1 Pita 1:14\x*‚ÄúFom…®ra gumazamiziba God g…®fozir puvat…®. Dughiar kam…®n, me fozir puvat…®gha amizir biziba, God dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n God Akar Gavgavim an…®ga ghaze, nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar dar itir gumazamiziba bar uan navibagh iragh.
\v 31 \x - \xo 17:31 \xt Onger Akaba 9:8; 96:13; Aposel 2:24; 10:42; Rom 2:16; 14:10\x*God gumazamizibar arazir kuraba bagh me tuis…®ghamin dughiam ak…®righa g…®fa. An arazir aghuim…®n m…®rara a inabazir gumazim, nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba tuis…®gham. Gumazir kam aremez…® God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi. Bizir kam…®n God e tuis…®ghamin ingangarim gumazamiziba bar men akaz…®, me fo, a guizbang…®ram otogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Egha me ua d…®kavamin m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha, marazi a d…®pofi. Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dughiatam ua bizir kam m…®k…®mt…®, e n…® baraghasa.‚Äù
\v 33 Ez…® Pol me ategha ghu.
\v 34 Ez…® gumazamizir maba Pol…®n n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghua n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an m…®g…®r…®g…®abar iti. Men tong…®n Dionisius, a Areopagus kaunsel…®n aven itir gumazir mam. Ez…® amizir mam, an ziam Damaris, a gumazamizir igharazir maba ko, me uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar iti.
\c 18
\s1 Pol Korin…®n nguibar ekiam…®n God…®n Akar Aghuim akuri
\p 
\v 1 Bizir kabar g…®n, Pol Atens ategha Korin…®n nguibam…®n ghu.
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Rom 16:3; 1 Korin 16:19; 2 Timoti 4:19\x*Egha a Judan gumazir mam bato, an ziam Akwila. An nguibam Pontus…®n Provins…®n aven iti. A uan amuim Prisila ko, aning mong fom…®ra kantri Italin ike, ez…® Sisar Klodius Judabav g…®a ghaze, me Rom…®n nguibar ekiam ategh igharagh mang…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning Itali ategha Korin…®n ize. Ez…® Pol aning ganasa zui.
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Aposel 20:34; 1 Korin 4:12; 1 Tesalonika 2:9; 2 Tesalonika 3:8\x*Pol uaghan aning…®n m…®rara, sel…®n d…®penibar ingari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an aning…®n ganasa ghugha, aning ko ikia egha me ko ingari.
\v 4 Sabat…®n dughiabar, Pol zurara Judaba God ko m…®geir d…®penibar ghua me ko uariv gei. A Judaba ko Grighbar n…®ghn…®zibar amut…®ma, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikiasa me gakaghori.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt Aposel 9:22; 17:3; 17:14-15; 18:28\x*Ez…® Sailas ko Timoti Masedonia ategha izaghir…®z…®, Pol dughiabar zurara God…®n Akar Aghuim akuri. An akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n derav…®ra Judabagh eghari, Iesus a Krais, Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Aposel 13:45-46; 13:51; 20:26; 1 Pita 4:4\x*Ez…® Judaba Pol…®n akam baraghan aghuagha, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kuraba a gan…®di. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan korotiam…®n m…®neziba ap…®zigha, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n ia God…®n saghon ik…® oveght…®, mar ian os…®mt…®zimra. Ez…® k…® uab…® os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n Akar Aghuim Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba me m…®k…®nam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Pol God ko m…®geir d…®penim ategha Titius Jastus…®n d…®penim…®n ghu. Gumazir kam zurara God…®n ziam fe. An d…®penim a Judaba God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n borogh…®n iti.
\v 8 \x - \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Korin 1:14\x*Krispus, God ko m…®geir d…®penibar garir gumazir dapanim. Ez…® a uan adarazi ko me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n iti. Ez…® Korin…®n gumazamizir av…®rim Pol…®n akam baregha, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikia egha rue.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Aposel 23:11; 1 Korin 2:3\x*Ez…® d…®magarir mam…®n Ekiam irebam…®n m…®n garir bizim…®n kamagh…®n Pol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®, n…® m…®k…®mv…®ra ik…®, egh n…®m…®ra ikian mark…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 18:10 \xt Josua 1:9; Aisaia 41:10; Jeremaia 1:8; 1:18-19; Matyu 28:20; Jon 10:16\x*K…® n…® ko iti, nan gumazamizir av…®riba nguibar ekiar kam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n tav paz…® n…® damighan kogh, egh n…® m…®sueghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 11 Ez…® Pol azenir vam…®ra ko akuam…®n ikiava, God…®n Akar Aghuim men sure gami.
\p 
\v 12 Galio, Akaian Provins…®n gavman…®n gumazir dapanim…®n itima, Judan gumaziba bar d…®kavigha Pol…®n apanim…®n gamua a isa kot gat…®.
\v 13 Me ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, a gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa Moses Osirizir Araziba riagh…®riagh…®va, arazir igharazim…®n God…®n ziam f…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 18:14 \xt Aposel 23:29; 25:11; 25:19\x*Pol bar men akam ikarvaghasava ami, ez…® Galio Judabav gei, ‚ÄúIa Judaba, gumazir kam Rom osirizir araziba abigham, o an arazir kuratam damight…®ma, k…® ian akam baregham.
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Jon 18:31; Aposel 23:29; 25:18-19\x*Ez…® ia m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko ziaba ko ia uan araziba, bagha n…®ghn…®gha na bagha izi. Markiam. Ia uari dar k…®rm…®gh. K…® bizir kabar kotiaba bareghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a me amadaz…®, me kot ategha azenan ize.
\v 17 Ez…® Korin…®n gumaziba, magh…®ra Sostenes…®n suira, a Judabar d…®penir God ko m…®geim…®n garir gumazir dapanim, egha kot…®n danganim borogh…®ra a m…®sosi. Ez…® Galio bizir me amizir kam gunuira.\f + \fr 18:17 \ft Grigh…®n akam deragha bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®. Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, Judaba uari uan gumazir dapanir ekiam…®n atarav egha me a m…®sosi.\f*
\s1 Pol uamategha Antiogh…®n nguibam ghu
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 18:18 \xt D…®boboniba 6:18; Aposel 21:24; Rom 16:1\x*Pol dughiar mabar Korin…®n ikegha, Krais…®n adarazi ategha kurim…®n ghuavanabogha Sirian Distrigh…®n ghu. Prisila koma Akwila a ko zui. Dughiar a t…®ghar kurim…®n mangamim, a Senkrian ikia God ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir mam gami. Kamagh…®n a uan dapanir ar…®zim gise.\f + \fr 18:18 \ft Judaba kamagh…®n ami, me God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®n mang…®va, uan dapanir ar…®zim gisegham.\f*
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt Aposel 17:17\x*Ez…® me Efesus otivigha, Pol Prisila ko Akwila kagh aning ataki. Egha a uab…® Judabar d…®penir God ko m…®geim…®n ghua me ko uariv gei.
\v 20 Ez…® me dughiar tabar uarir gan ikiasava a m…®geima, a ghaze, Puvat…®.
\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Rom 1:10; 1 Korin 4:19; Hibru 6:3; Jems 4:15\x*A me atagh…®ragha, akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod ifueght…®, k…® ua ia bagh izam.‚Äù Egha kurim inigha Efesus ategha ghu.
\v 22 Egha a Sisarian otogha, Jerusalem…®n itir Krais…®n adarazigh etiasa ghuavanabo. Egha g…®n Antiogh…®n nguibam…®n ghuaghir…®.
\p 
\v 23 Pol dughiar mabar Antiogh…®n ikegha, Distrik Galesia ko Frigian itir nguibaba bar dagh arua, men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir Iesus…®n itiba gavgavim me gan…®di.
\s1 Apolos God…®n Akar Aghuim Efesus…®n nguibam…®n anekuri
\p 
\v 24 Judan gumazir mam, an ziam Apolos, an Aleksandrian gumazim. A iza Efesus…®n nguibam…®n iti. A bar derav…®ra m…®g…®ava, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n Osiziriba bar dagh fo.
\v 25 \x - \xo 18:25 \xt Aposel 19:3; Rom 12:11\x*Me Ekiam…®n tuavim…®n a geghani, ez…® a gumazamizibar sure damuasa an navim bar a d…®kafi. A bar derav…®ra Iesus amizir bizibar me m…®gei. Egha a Jon…®n rurimra fo.
