\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Daniel 12:2; Jon 5:28-29; Aposel 23:6; 26:6-7; 28:20\x*Ez…® k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia kamagh…®n fo, a gumazir ovengezibar amut…® me ua d…®kavam. Gumazir aghuiba ko kuraba sara. A damuamin bizim, k…® a bagha m…®zuai. Ez…® akam na gasir gumaziba uaghan bizir kam bagha m…®zuai iti.
