\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17 \xt Aposel 11:29-30; 20:16; Rom 15:25-26; 2 Korin 8:4; Galesia 2:10\x*\x - \xo 24:17-18 \xt Aposel 21:17-28\x*‚ÄúEgha k…® azenir mabar nguibar igharazibar ikegha, uamategha Jerusalem…®n ize. K…® God dan…®ngamin ofaba ko gumazamizir onganarazibar akurvaghasa dag…®aba inigha izi.
\v 18 Ez…® k…® God…®n D…®penim…®n itima me nan gari k…® God…®n damazim…®n zue. Gumazir av…®rim na ko itir puvat…®z…®, n…®g…®nir av…®riba uaghan puvat…®.\f + \fr 24:18 \ft Tertulus ves 6…®n aven Pol akam a gasa ghaze, Pol God…®n D…®penim damut…®, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham. Ez…® Pol akar kam ikarvaghasa, kamagh…®n m…®gei, a zuegha g…®vagha g…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n aven zui.\f*
\v 19 \x - \xo 24:19 \xt Aposel 23:30; 25:16; 2 Timoti 1:15\x*Ez…® Judan gumazir Esian itir maba, me iza nan suiki, kamagh…®n me akatam nan ik…®, me uari kagh iz…®va, n…®n damazim…®n na is…® kot dar…®gh.
\v 20 Ez…® dughiar k…® Judan kot…®n aven tughav itim, gumazir kagh itir kaba me nan gari arazir kurar manam nan iti, me n…® m…®k…®m.
\v 21 \x - \xo 24:21 \xt Aposel 23:6; 28:20\x*Ez…® k…® men tong…®n tughav ikia d…®a m…®kemezir akam, me ti a gifongezir puvat…®. Akar kam, ‚ÄòGumazir ovengeziba ua d…®kavam, ez…® bizir kam bagha me na inigha ian kot dar…®ghasa ize.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 24:22 \xt Aposel 23:26\x*Feliks men n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba ko arazir me Ekiam…®n g…®n zuir Tuavim g…®fogha g…®fa. Ez…® Pol m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Feliks Judabav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa orarkegh. M…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanim, Lisias, iz…®t…®ma, k…® ian m…®g…®r…®g…®abar k…®ram.‚Äù
\v 23 \x - \xo 24:23 \xt Aposel 27:3; 28:16; 28:30\x*Egha a Pol kalabus dar…®ghasa m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanim m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® kalabus…®n gavgavim Pol damuan mark…®. Pol…®n namakaba bizibar an akurvaght…® n…® men anogoroghan mark…®.
\s1 Feliks Pol…®n t…®vaz…® an azenir pumuning…®n kalabus…®n iti
\p 
\v 24 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Feliks uan amuim Drusila ko ize. A Judan amizim. Ez…® Feliks Pol…®n diagha an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba barazi a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n itir arazibav gei.
\v 25 Ez…® Pol God…®n damazim…®n derazir arazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am gamua navir ghurim…®n arazim d…®kab…®rir arazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am gamua, God…®n Kotiar G…®n Izamin m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh ami. Ez…® Feliks bizir kam baregha atiatigha ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra tuz…®, n…® mang…®. K…® g…®n dughiatam ik…® ua n…®n diagham.‚Äù
\v 26 Ez…® dughiar kamra Feliks…®n n…®ghn…®zim ghaze, Pol dag…®ataba inigh a danight…® a Pol ateght…®ma a mangam. Bizir kam bagha dughiar av…®ribar a Pol…®n deima, a iza a ko m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh ami.
