\v 27 \x - \xo 24:27 \xt Aposel 25:9; 25:14\x*Ez…® azenir pumuning g…®vaz…®ma, Porsius Festus a Feliks…®n danganim ini. Feliks Judabar amut…® me a bagh bar akueghasa, a Pol ataghiz…® a kalabus…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\c 25
\s1 Pol ghaze, Sisar nan kotiam baragham
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Festus Judian Distrigh…®n izez…®, dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaz…®ma a Sisaria ategha Jerusalem…®n ghuavanadi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 25:2 \xt Aposel 24:1; 25:15\x*Festus Jerusalem…®n ghuavanaboz…®, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar gumazir dapaniba Festus…®n kotiam…®n tugha akaba Pol gasi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 25:3 \xt Aposel 23:12; 23:15\x*Me pamtem…®n kamagh…®n Festus m…®gei, n…® en akuragh gumazir kam amadaght…®, a Jerusalem…®n ghuavanang. Me gumazir mabav g…®a ghaze, ia Pol m…®sueght…® an aremeghs…®, mang…® an aravagh mongegh. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me kamagh…®n Festus m…®gei.
\v 4 Ez…® Festus me ikara, ‚ÄúPol a Sisarian kalabus…®n iti. Ez…® k…® gurumra Sisarian mag…®ram.
\v 5 Pol guizbang…®n os…®mt…®zim damight…®, ia akam a gas…®s…®, ian gumazir dapanir taba nan g…®n Sisarian mag…®r…® kotiam baragh.‚Äù
