\v 8 \x - \xo 25:8 \xt Aposel 24:12; 28:17\x*Ez…® Pol ua bagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Judabar arazitam ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Egha God…®n D…®penim gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®, egha os…®mt…®zitam Sisar gat…®zir puvat…®.‚Äù
