\v 9 \x - \xo 25:9 \xt Aposel 24:27; 25:20\x*Ez…® Festus Judabar akurvaghasa n…®ghn…®gha Pol…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® kotiam bagh Jerusalem…®n ghuavanaboght…®, k…® munagh akar me n…® gasiba baragham? N…® kamagh…®n ifongez, o?‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Pol a ikara, ‚ÄúKot…®n k…® tughav itir kam, kar Sisar…®n kotiam. Kot…®n kamra, kar nan kot. N…® uaghan bar fo, k…® os…®mt…®zitam…®n Judabagh amizir puvat…®.
\v 11 \x - \xo 25:11 \xt Aposel 23:11; 23:29; 25:25; 26:31-32; 28:19\x*K…® guizbang…®ra ovengamin arazitam damigh…®va ovengam. K…® ovevem…®n ar…®mang…®ghan kogham. Ez…® Judaba na gasir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da m…®ngariba puvat…®ght…®, tav na inigh Judabar dafarim dat…®ghan kogham. Sisar nan kotiam baraghasa k…® ifonge!‚Äù\f + \fr 25:11 \ft Rom…®n Arazibar mam ghaze, Rom…®n gumazitam n…®ghn…®si, kot…®n aven me deragha an akam baraghizir puvat…®, eght…® a kot…®n azaraght…®, Sisar uab…® an kotiam baragham. Sisar, a Rombar atrivibar ziam.\f*
\p 
\v 12 Festus a ko kotiam barazir gumazibar n…®ghn…®zim inigha, kamagh…®n Pol m…®gei, ‚ÄúSisar n…®n kotiam baraghs…®, n…® Sisar bagh mang…®!‚Äù
