\v 13 Ez…® dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Atrivim Agripa uan amuim Bernaisi ko aning Festus…®n gan dughiar aghuim a dan…®ngasa Sisarian zui.\f + \fr 25:13 \ft Atrivim Agripa, a Atrivim Herot…®n otarim. Atrivim Herot faragha Jon…®n dozim Jems m…®soghez…® an areme. N…® akar Aposel 12 v…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 14 \x - \xo 25:14 \xt Aposel 24:27\x*Aning dughiar av…®ribar Sisarian itima Festus Pol…®n gun Atrivim Agripa m…®gei. Festus ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir mam kagh iti. Feliks a isa kalabus gat…®z…® a ikiav…®ra ikia kagh iti.
\v 15 K…® Jerusalem…®n itima ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judabar gumazir aruaba akaba a gasa nan azangs…®gha ghaze, k…® an os…®mt…®zim gun m…®kemeght…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.
