\v 19 \x - \xo 25:19 \xt Aposel 18:15; 23:29\x*Judaba uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba bagha Pol ko uari adosi. Egha aremezir gumazir mam Iesus, Pol ghaze, an angam…®ra itima me bizir kam bagha uari adosi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 25:20 \xt Aposel 25:9\x*K…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim buriava avenge. K…® deragha fozir puvat…®. Egha kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄòN…® ti Jerusalem…®n mang…®va akar me n…® gasir kaba bagh kotiam damu?‚Äô
\v 21 Ez…® Pol ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® kalabus…®n ikiam, eght…® g…®n Sisar nan kotiam baragham.‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® me m…®kemez…®, me an suiraz…® a kalabus…®n iti. Eght…® k…® g…®n tuavitam batogh Sisar bagh anemangam.‚Äù
