\v 27 ‚ÄúNan n…®ghn…®zim, k…® pura kalabuziar gumazitam amang, an arazim…®n gun osirighan koght…®, kar arazir aghuim puvat…®.‚Äù
\c 26
\s1 Pol Agripa m…®gei
