\v 9 \x - \xo 26:9 \xt 1 Timoti 1:13\x*\x - \xo 26:9-11 \xt Aposel 8:3; 22:4-5\x*‚ÄúFom…®ra k…® uab…® ghaze, k…® bizir bar av…®ribar amut…® da Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®gham.
