\v 20 \x - \xo 26:20 \xt Matyu 3:8; Aposel 9:20; 9:28-29; 11:26; 13:14\x*Egha k…® faragha Damaskus…®n nguibam…®n akam akuni, egha Jerusalem…®n akam akunigha, Judan nguibaba bar dar akam akurava, uaghan Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba sara akam me m…®k…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄòIa uan navibagh iragh ua God bagh iz…®. Eght…® ian arazir ia amiba, ian gun m…®k…®m suam, ia navibagh iragha g…®fa.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 26:21 \xt Aposel 21:30-31\x*K…® bizir kabar akam akurima, Judaba na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa, me God…®n D…®penir av…®zibar nan suira.
\v 22 \x - \xo 26:22 \xt Luk 24:27; 24:44; Jon 5:46; Rom 3:21\x*God nan akuraz…® k…® deragha ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n, egha k…® kagh tughav ikia akam me m…®gei, gumazir k…®niba ko gumazir ekiaba me bar. Akar kamra, Moses ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba fom…®ra an gun m…®keme. K…® uam akar igharazitam akuri puvat…®.
