\v 24 \x - \xo 27:24 \xt Aposel 23:11\x*‚ÄòPol, n…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® mang…®t…®, Sisar n…®n kotiam baragh. N…® oragh, God n…®n azangs…®zim baregha g…®vagha n…®n apangkufi. Gumazir n…® ko kurim…®n itiba, me oveghan kogham.‚Äô
\v 25 \x - \xo 27:25 \xt Rom 4:20-21; 2 Timoti 1:12\x*Gumaziba, ia oragh! K…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia kamagh…®n fo, God na m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra biziba otivam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gavgavigh atiatingan mark…®.
