\v 17 \x - \xo 28:17 \xt Aposel 21:33; 24:12-13; 25:8\x*Ez…® 3pla dughiaba g…®vaz…®ma, Pol Judan gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa. Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan aveghbuaba, k…® bizitam e uan adarazi paza me gamizir puvat…®, o en ovavibar arazitam iriazir puvat…®. Ez…® me Jerusalem…®n na kalabus gat…®ghava, na isa Rom…®n gumazibar dafarim gat…®.
